Fuss-ronald-reagan-aircraft-carrier-ends-yearslong-pacific-stint-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUSS%20Ronald%20Reagan%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223e75f4fc-65a2-4941-9025-8968113d1a40%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20separated%20from%20the%20military%20in%202021%20to%20pursue%20real%20estate%20full-time%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20Navy%20job%20included%20writing%20press%20releases%2C%20aerial%20photography%2C%20videography%2C%20and%20printing.%20In%20later%20years%2C%20I%20was%20stationed%20at%20the%20Naval%20Hospital%20Balboa%20in%20San%20Diego%2C%20where%20we%20covered%20COVID-19%2C%20and%20I%20was%20deployed%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-navy-hospital-ship-usns-mercy-stops-receiving-patients-2020-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUSNS%20Mercy%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20San%20Pedro%20in%20Los%20Angeles%20during%20the%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20presented%20with%20an%20%26quot%3Bearly%20out%26quot%3B%20program%20because%20of%20overmanning%20in%20my%20job%2C%20and%20it%20allowed%20me%20to%20complete%20my%20contract%20a%20couple%20of%20years%20early.%20I%20had%20already%20started%20my%20business%2C%20but%20leaving%20the%20military%20allowed%20me%20to%20pursue%20it%20full-time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20wanted%20to%20spend%20more%20time%20with%20my%20young%20family.%20My%20eldest%20was%20born%20in%20January%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cb716fd3-246e-4a67-9cd0-dd90658b27b0%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMy%20wife%20and%20I%20met%20on%20the%20day%20I%20arrived%20on%20the%20USS%20Ronald%20Reagan%20in%202016%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20became%20friends%20through%20the%20first-response%2Ffirefighting%20team%2C%20where%20she%20worked%20as%20an%20electrician.%20We%20also%20noticed%20each%20other%20at%20church%20services%2C%20and%20she%20invited%20me%20to%20her%20baptism%20ceremony%2C%20where%20she%20was%20baptized%20inside%20an%20open%20jet%20fuel%20tank.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarly%20in%20our%20relationship%2C%20we%20lived%20together%20in%20a%20small%20Japanese%20apartment.%20Then%2C%20we%20spent%20about%20a%20year%20doing%20long-distance%2C%20with%20me%20still%20deploying%20on%20the%20carrier%20and%20her%20based%20in%20San%20Diego.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20year%20of%20dating%2C%20we%20got%20married%2C%20and%20soon%20after%20some%20vacation%20in%20the%20US%2C%20we%20discovered%20we%20were%20expecting%20our%20first%20child.%20During%20most%20of%20her%20pregnancy%2C%20Theressa%20lived%20alone%20until%20I%20got%20stationed%20in%20San%20Diego%20around%20her%20seventh%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20same%20year%2C%20I%20became%20deeply%20interested%20in%20personal%20finance%20and%20real-estate%20investing%2C%20inspired%20by%20stories%20of%20blue-collar%20workers%20achieving%20financial%20freedom%20through%20real%20estate.%20I%20learned%20the%20most%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.biggerpockets.com%2Fpodcasts%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBiggerPockets%3C%2Fa%3E%20podcasts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226e0d19c2-5872-4601-9568-7557ca8fd3f3%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20were%20motivated%20to%20become%20first-time%20homebuyers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20were%20eager%20to%20apply%20what%20we%20had%20learned%20and%20planned%20to%20use%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fused-va-loan-buy-property-2022-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVA%20loan%20entitlement%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20our%20military%20service.%20VA%20entitlement%20is%20how%20much%20lenders%20can%20lend%20to%20a%20veteran%20or%20active%20duty%20member%20without%20providing%20a%20down%20payment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20aimed%20to%20buy%20a%20multifamily%20property%20%E2%80%94%20ideally%20a%20duplex%2C%20triplex%2C%20or%20fourplex%20%E2%80%94%20so%20we%20could%20live%20in%20one%20unit%20and%20rent%20the%20others%20to%20offset%20our%20mortgage.%20Today%2C%20this%20strategy%20is%20known%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freal-estate-investing-for-beginners-investors-house-hacking-strategy%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehouse%20hacking%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225eead5bb-9c0b-4dea-9d2e-6a72780335b3%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBeing%20stationed%20in%20San%20Diego%20gave%20us%20a%20few%20key%20advantages%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20housing%20allowance%20we%20received%20as%20military%20members%20was%20higher%20than%20in%20most%20US%20locations%2C%20boosting%20our%20household%20income%20to%20about%20%2410%2C000-%2412%2C000%20monthly.%20This%20allowance%20was%20discontinued%20once%20we%20both%20left%20the%20military.%20Theressa%20left%20the%20Navy%20almost%20a%20year%20before%20I%20did%20at%20the%20end%20of%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESecond%2C%20the%20VA%20loan%20allowed%20us%20to%20buy%20a%20multifamily%20property%20with%20zero%20down%20payment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThird%2C%20we%20included%2075%25%20of%20the%20gross%20rental%20income%20from%20the%20property%20in%20our%20loan%20application%2C%20increasing%20our%20approved%20loan%20amount.%20On%20paper%2C%20our%20monthly%20gross%20increased%20to%20%2415%2C000-%2417%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20new%20legislation%20removed%20local%20VA%20loan%20limits%20for%20first-time%20users%2C%20giving%20us%20more%20purchasing%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a88636f1-5145-4b24-96ad-772059dfe341%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAfter%20months%20of%20searching%2C%20we%20found%20a%20triplex%20listed%20for%20%241.2%20million%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20offered%20%241%20million%20and%20settled%20at%20%241.1%20million.%20By%20March%202020%2C%20we%20had%20moved%20into%20a%20three-bedroom%20unit%20while%20renting%20out%20the%20other%20two%20for%20about%20%244%2C000%20a%20month%2C%20reducing%20our%20housing%20costs%20to%20less%20than%20what%20one-bedroom%20rentals%20were%20going%20for%20at%20the%20time.%20This%20was%20the%20start%20of%20Semi%20Homes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20liv