F%2Fwww.defensenews.com%2Fglobal%2Fmideast-africa%2F2024%2F12%2F13%2Fkurdish-forces-in-syria-accidentally-shot-down-us-reaper-drone%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Econfirmed%20to%20Defense%20News%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20the%20SDF%20misidentified%20the%20MQ-9%20as%20a%20threat%20on%20December%209%20and%20shot%20it%20down%2C%20without%20specifying%20what%20kind%20of%20weapon%20was%20used%3B%20the%20SDF%20hasn't%20publicly%20acknowledged%20the%20incident.%20However%2C%20the%20SDF%20did%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FSDF_Syria%2Fstatus%2F1866508054927491400%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Erelease%20footage%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20purportedly%20showing%20its%20forces%20shooting%20down%20Turkey's%20Aksungur%20drone.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BThe%20SDF%20would%20need%20more%20capable%20air%20defense%20systems%20than%20older%20MANPADs%20(man-portable%20air%20defense%20system)%20like%20the%20Strela-2%20to%20shoot%20down%20an%20MQ-9%20Reaper%20unless%20the%20drone%20was%20flying%20far%20below%20its%20typical%20operating%20ceiling%2C%20possibly%20due%20to%20mission%20requirements%20or%20technical%20issues%2C%26quot%3B%20Freddy%20Khoueiry%2C%20a%20global%20security%20analyst%20for%20the%20Middle%20East%20and%20North%20Africa%20at%20the%20risk%20intelligence%20company%20RANE%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20Reaper%20drone%20has%20a%2066-foot%20wingspan%20and%20can%20fly%20up%20to%2050%2C000%20feet%20in%20altitude%2C%20beyond%20the%20range%20of%20shoulder-fired%20Strela-2%20missiles.%20The%20remotely%20piloted%20aircraft%20frequently%20carry%20Hellfire%20ground-attack%20missiles.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BA%20SHORAD%20(short-range%20air%20defense)%20or%20medium-range%20radar-guided%20SAM%20(surface-to-air%20missile)%20system%20would%20be%20required%20to%20effectively%20engage%20a%20Reaper%20drone%20operating%20at%20its%20standard%20altitude%2C%26quot%3B%20Khoueiry%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20more%20likely%20that%20the%20SDF%20has%20shoulder-fired%20missiles%20due%20to%20their%20proliferation%2C%20which%20also%20have%20the%20benefit%20of%20being%20harder%20to%20spot%20than%20truck-mounted%20missile%20launchers.%20If%20the%20MQ-9%20was%20downed%20by%20a%20MANPAD%2C%20it%20suggests%20it%20was%20flying%20very%20low%2C%20Khoueiry%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20US%20Air%20Force%20MQ-9%20Reaper%20flew%20over%20central%20New%20York%20during%20a%20training%20flight%20on%20Oct.%2031.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F676209dd1d90e3bcf31d7978%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221331%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20US%20Air%20Force%20MQ-9%20Reaper%20flew%20over%20central%20New%20York%20during%20a%20training%20flight%20on%20Oct.%2031.%3Cp%3ETech.%20Sgt.%20Alexander%20Rector%2FUS%20Air%20Force%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Aksungur%20is%20a%20much%20larger%20and%20more%20advanced%20drone%20than%20Turkey's%20widely%20exported%20Bayraktar%20TB2%2C%20but%20it%20is%20not%20in%20the%20same%20league%20as%20the%20American%20MQ-9.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BAksungur%20drones%20are%20capable%2C%20'middle-class%20drones'%20that%20are%20typically%20used%20for%20intelligence%2C%20surveillance%2C%20and%20reconnaissance%2C%20although%20increasingly%20modified%20to%20carry%20weapons%2C%26quot%3B%20Nicholas%20Heras%2C%20senior%20director%20of%20strategy%20and%20innovation%20at%20the%20New%20Lines%20Institute%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESyrian%20soldiers%20abandoned%20their%20bases%20and%20weapons%20stockpiles%20during%20the%20dramatic%20fall%20of%20President%20Bashar%20al-Assad's%20regime%20in%20early%20December.%20Israel%20has%20already%20moved%20in%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fisraeli-airstrike-syria-assad-military-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ebombed%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20large%20quantities%20of%20them.%20Turkey%20has%20also%20moved%20to%20prevent%20the%20SDF%20from%20capturing%20weapons.%20Turkish%20intelligence%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fturkey-hits-military-supplies-under-kurdish-control-north-syria-security-source-2024-12-10%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edestroyed%2012%20trucks%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20with%20missiles%20and%20other%20heavy%20weapons%20in%20the%20northeastern%20Kurdish%20city%20of%20Qamishli%2C%20and%20Turkish%20drones%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.syriahr.com%2Fen%2F351430%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Etargeted%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20abandoned%20tanks%2C%20armored%20vehicles%2C%20and%20rocket%20launchers%20strewn%20across%20northeast%20Syria.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20unlikely%20that%20the%20SDF%20captured%20and%20were%20able%20to%20quickly%20operationalize%20Syrian%20regime%20air%20defenses%20within%20the%20past%20week%2C%26quot%3B%20RANE's%20Khoueiry%20said.%20%26quot%3BFurthermore%2C%20Israeli%20strikes%20have%20significantly%20degraded%20such%20systems%20across%20Syrian%20territory%2C%20making%20it%20even%20more%20difficult%20for%20a%20US-backed%20militia%20to%20acquire%20and%20effectively%20operate%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETurkish%20media%20reported%20earlier%20this%20year%20that%20US%20troops%20in%20northeast%20Syria%20were%20training%20the%20SDF%20how%20to%20use%20the%20AN%2FTWQ-1%20Avenger%20short-range%20air%20defense%20system%2C%20which%20fires%20Stinger%20missiles.%20However%2C%20sources%20in%20Syria%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.syriahr.com%2Fen%2F341843%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ecited%20by%20the%20UK-based%20Syrian%20Observatory%20for%20Human%20Rights%20war%20monitor%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20said%20only%20US%20troops%20operate%20the%20Avengers%2C%20which%20protect%20their%20bases%20against%20Iran-backed%20militia%20drone%20attacks.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BThe%20challenge%20for%20the%20SDF%20to%20use%20systems%20such%20as%20the%20SA-2s%20(Soviet-made%20S-75s)%20or%20Avengers%20is%20that%20these%20anti-air%20systems%20require%20a%20logistical%20network%20to%20operate%20that%20is%20cumbersome%20for%20a%20non-state%20actor%2C%20especially%20if%20that%20non-state%20actor%20doesn't%20have%20accompanying%20anti-air%20capabilities%20to%20protect%20those%20systems%2C%26quot%3B%20Heras%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECeng%20Sagnic%2C%20chief%20of%20analysis%20of%20the%20geopolitical%20consultancy%20firm%20TAM-C%20Solutions%2C%20believes%20it%20is%20possible%20the%20SDF%20is%20%26quot%3Bindependently%20operating%26quot%3B%20some%20air%20defenses%20in%20Syria.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20it%20should%20be%20noted%20that%20Kurdish%20groups%20have%20long%20had%20access%20to%20short-range%20air%20defense%20missiles%2C%20particularly%20those%20acquired%20from%20the%20black%20market%20and%20not%20NATO%20standard%2C%26quot%3B%20Sagnic%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20also%20a%20possibility%20that%20an%20operator%20of%20one%20of%20these%20systems%20got%20lucky%20that%20day.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BIn%20any%20case%2C%20the%20incident%20demonstrates%20the%20readiness%20of%20Kurdish%20groups%20in%20Syria%20to%20respond%20to%20drone%20operations%2C%20especially%20those%20conducted%20by%20Turkey%2C%26quot%3B%20Sagnic%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Kurdistan%20Workers%20Party%2C%20commonly%20known%20by%20its%20PKK%20acronym%2C%20had%20Strela-2%20missiles%20as%20far%20back%20as%20the%201990s%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fnews%2Fworldviews%2Fwp%2F2016%2F05%2F14%2Fkurdish-militants-just-challenged-turkish-air-power-in-a-major-way%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eshot%20down%20two%20Turkish%20helicopters%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20over%20northern%20Iraq%20in%201997.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Middle%20East%20Eye%20news%20outlet%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.middleeasteye.net%2Fnews%2Fpkk-new-tech-fuels-turkey-suspicions-iran%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereported%20earlier%20this%20year%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20Iran%20had%20transferred%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdrone-hunting-drones-are-already-impacting-middle-east-conflicts-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eair-breathing%20anti-drone%20loitering%20missiles%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20the%20PKK.%20One%20such%20munition%20purportedly%20brought%20down%20an%20Aksungur%20over%20Iraqi%20Kurdistan%20in%20May.%20Iran-backed%20Hezbollah%20in%20Lebanon%20and%20the%20Houthis%20in%20Yemen%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.haaretz.com%2Fisrael-news%2Fsecurity-aviation%2F2023-11-29%2Fty-article%2Fsaqr-358-iran-hezbollah-loitering-missile-israel-us-uavs-yemen-houthis%2F0000018c-1ac5-d3b6-adef-bbfd2efd0000%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehave%20used%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20Iranian-made%20358%20missile%20to%20shoot%20down%20Israeli%20and%20American%20drones%2C%20including%20a%20number%20of%20MQ-9s.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt's%20unclear%20if%20the%20SDF%20%E2%80%94%20whose%20main%20Kurdish%20component%20Turkey%20charges%20with%20inextricable%20PKK%20links%20%E2%80%94%20acquired%20such%20a%20system.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BThe%20claim%20that%20Iran%20supplies%20the%20PKK%20(and%2C%20by%20extension%2C%20the%20SDF)%20with%20a%20significant%20number%20of%20anti-drone%20missiles%20is%20highly%20questionable%2C%26quot%3B%20Sagnic%20said.%20%26quot%3BOnly%20a%20consistent%20pattern%20of%20successful%20anti-drone%20strikes%20by%20the%20SDF%20in%20the%20near%20future%20could%20indicate%20enhanced%20capabilities%20by%20the%20Kurdish%20group%2C%20and%20a%20single%20drone%20interception%20is%20not%20sufficient%20proof.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20there%20have%20been%20at%20least%20two%20reported%20interceptions%20of%20Turkish%20drones%20over%20northern%20Iraq%20in%20recent%20months%2C%20suggesting%20that%20Kurdish%20groups%20are%20adapting%20to%20the%20so-called%20drone%20wars%2C%20though%20their%20continued%20success%20remains%20uncertain.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EPaul%20Iddon%20is%20a%20freelance%20journalist%20and%20columnist%20who%20writes%20about%20Middle%20East%20developments%2C%20military%20affairs%2C%20politics%2C%20and%20history.%20His%20articles%20have%20appeared%20in%20a%20variety%20of%20publications%20focused%20on%20the%20region.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-sdf-syria-may-have-downed-reaper-drone-2024-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734516061000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F676203bcccd8dfcfcd7fbdff%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-sdf-syria-may-have-downed-reaper-drone-2024-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20US's%20advanced%20MQ-9%20Reaper%20drone%20suffered%20another%20downing%2C%20this%20time%20at%20the%20hands%20of%20its%20partner%20in%20Syria.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Paul%20Iddon)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-sdf-syria-may-have-downed-reaper-drone-2024-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%2