cture%20to%20develop%20AI%20models%20and%20apps%2C%20resulting%20from%20a%20multi-year%20effort%20across%20teams.%20It%20ultimately%20aims%20to%20become%20companies'%20one-stop-shop%20for%20tech%20needs%20like%20training%20AI%20for%20drug%20discovery%20and%20building%20apps%20for%20health%20coaching.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20unit%20is%20also%20looking%20to%20raise%20another%20round%20of%20capital%20in%20the%20next%20year%2C%20the%20two%20people%20familiar%20with%20the%20matter%20said.%20The%20company's%20last%20investment%20was%20a%20%241%20billion%20round%20led%20by%20Alphabet%20in%202022.%20Alphabet%20will%20likely%20lead%20the%20round%20again%2C%20although%20leadership%20could%20also%20bid%20for%20outside%20capital%20as%20Verily%20tries%20to%20become%20%26quot%3Bincreasingly%20independent%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20source%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20question%20for%20next%20year%20is%20whether%20Verily%20can%20finally%20start%20turning%20long-gestating%20ideas%20into%20profits.%20One%20of%20the%20people%20said%20Verily%20still%20generates%20the%20most%20revenue%20selling%20stop-loss%20insurance%20to%20employers%2C%20which%20is%20a%20far%20cry%20from%20the%20higher-margin%20business%20it's%20aiming%20for.%20The%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Ftech%2Falphabets-verily-plans-cost-cuts-amid-pressure-on-other-bets-to-rein-in-spending-fe7b3fa%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported%20last%20year%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20this%20business%2C%20called%20Granular%20Insurance%2C%20was%20Verily's%20most%20lucrative.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVerily%20has%20been%20criticized%20in%20the%20past%20for%20having%20a%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.statnews.com%2F2021%2F09%2F08%2Fverily-mega-abernethy-baseline%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erudderless%20strategy%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It's%20entertained%20bets%20on%20topics%20as%20diverse%20as%20editing%20mosquito%20populations%20and%20helping%20pharmaceutical%20companies%20run%20clinical%20trials.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20email%20to%20Business%20Insider%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20Verily%20declined%20to%20comment%20on%20non-public%20information.%20He%20confirmed%20the%20company's%20plans%20to%20provide%20tech%20infrastructure%20for%20third%20parties%2C%20designed%20to%20provide%20%26quot%3Bprecision%20health%20capabilities%20across%20research%20and%20care.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Verily%20campus%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5f15eeaf191824737674bcc7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EVerily's%20South%20San%20Francisco%20campus%3Cp%3ETada%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22762e24bb-6573-4542-80b1-7ce34cdfc922%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20AI%20strategy's%20origin%20story%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EVerily's%20idea%20to%20become%20a%20tech%20provider%20for%20other%20healthcare%20companies%20grew%20out%20of%20its%20own%20internal%20needs%20a%20few%20years%20ago%20when%20it%20decided%20to%20%26quot%3Bre-platform%26quot%3B%20its%20various%20bets%20on%20a%20shared%20infrastructure%2C%20a%20source%20familiar%20with%20the%20matter%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20multi-year%20effort%20is%20now%20coming%20to%20fruition%2C%20and%20Verily%20plans%20to%20sell%20the%20core%20technology%20it%20uses%20to%20health%20plans%2C%20providers%2C%20digital%20health%20startups%2C%20and%20life%20sciences%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20platform%20will%20include%20data%20storage%20and%20AI%20training.%20Companies%20could%20also%20use%20Verily's%20tech%20tools%20to%20spin%20up%20apps%20without%20having%20to%20code%20as%20much.%20For%20example%2C%20a%20digital%20health%20startup%20could%20use%20Verily's%20tools%20to%20build%20a%20coaching%20app%20with%20AI%20insights%20on%20weight%20loss.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLarge%20pharma%20companies%2C%20for%20example%2C%20look%20at%20the%20work%20we%20do%20and%20recognize%20that%20the%20data%20science%20applications%20or%20clinical%20research%20tools%20that%20they%20need%20to%20build%20themselves%20could%20be%20better%20if%20they%20were%20built%20using%20our%20platform%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Verily%20CEO%20Stephen%20Gillett%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.onyxnewsroom.com%2Falphabets-verily-is-the-future-of-precision-and-public-health%2F%23and-you%25E2%2580%2599re-a-gamer%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ein%20an%20interview%20with%20Fortune%20in%20November.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20that%20interview%2C%20Gillett%20said%20Verily's%20tech%20tools%20would%20include%20sophisticated%20AI%20capabilities%20for%20healthcare%2C%20data%20aggregation%2C%20privacy%2C%20and%20consent.%20One%20source%20said%20the%20company%20plans%20to%20start%20rolling%20them%20out%20in%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221125%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Myoung%20Cha%2C%20Verily's%20chief%20product%20officer%2C%20joined%20from%20startup%20Carbon%20Health.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F609ae40bba78eb001906ebfb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221490%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMyoung%20Cha%2C%20Verily's%20chief%20product%20officer%2C%20joined%20from%20startup%20Carbon%20Health.%3Cp%3ECarbon%20Health%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20as%20the%20leading%20AI%20models%20learn%20from%20the%20entirety%20of%20the%20internet%2C%20healthcare%20data%20remains%20largely%20private.%20Subsequently%2C%20Verily%20is%20betting%20that%20there's%20a%20growing%20need%20to%20further%20specialize%20the%20models%20for%20patient%20care%20and%20research.%20The%20upstart%20already%20does%20this%20work%20through%20its%20partnership%20with%20clients%20like%20the%20National%20Institutes%20of%20Health.%20Through%20a%20business%20line%20called%20Workbench%2C%20Verily%20hosts%20massive%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fallofus.nih.gov%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edatasets%3C%2Fa%