20technology%20exactly%20for%20the%20opportunity%20that%20is%20coming%20in%202025%2C%20Mark%20Heaps%2C%20Groq's%20%26quot%3Bchief%20tech%20evangelist%26quot%3B%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b77c9d49-4307-4c1c-80e6-3abd11e1fbf1%5C%22%3E'Unleashing%20the%20beast'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20we%20decided%20to%20do%20was%20take%20all%20of%20our%20compute%2C%20make%20it%20available%20via%20a%20cloud%20instance%2C%20and%20we%20gave%20it%20away%20to%20the%20world%20for%20free%2C%26quot%3B%20Heaps%20said.%20Internally%2C%20the%20team%20called%20the%20strategy%2C%20%26quot%3Bunleashing%20the%20beast%26quot%3B.%20Groq's%20free%20tier%20caps%20users%20at%20a%20ceiling%20marked%20by%20requests%20per%20day%20or%20tokens%20per%20minute.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHeaps%2C%20CEO%20and%20ex-Googler%20Jonathan%20Ross%2C%20and%20a%20relatively%20lean%20team%20have%20spent%202023%20and%202024%20recruiting%20developers%20to%20try%20Groq's%20tech.%20Through%20hackathons%20and%20contests%2C%20the%20company%20makes%20a%20promise%20%E2%80%94%20try%20the%20hardware%20via%20Groq's%20cloud%20platform%20for%20free%2C%20and%20break%20through%20walls%20you've%20hit%20with%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGroq%20offers%20some%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-competition-sambanova-groq-cerebras-show-faster-inference-speed-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efastest%20inference%3C%2Fa%3E%20out%20there%2C%20according%20to%20rankings%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2FArtificialanalysis.ai%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EArtificialanalysis.ai%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20measures%20cost%20and%20latency%20for%20companies%20that%20allow%20users%20to%20buy%20access%20to%20specific%20models%20by%20the%20token%20%E2%80%94%20or%20output.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-competition-sambanova-groq-cerebras-show-faster-inference-speed-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInference%20%3C%2Fa%3Eis%20a%20type%20of%20computing%20that%20produces%20the%20answers%20to%20queries%20asked%20of%20large%20language%20models.%20Training%2C%20the%20more%20energy%3Cstrong%3E-%3C%2Fstrong%3Eintensive%20type%20of%20computing%2C%20is%20what%20gives%20the%20models%20the%20ability%20to%20answer.%20So%20far%2C%20the%20hardware%20used%20for%20those%20two%20tasks%20has%20been%20different.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHeaps%20and%20several%20of%20his%20Nvidia-challenging%20cohorts%20at%20companies%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-cuda-software-gpu-ai-chips-cerebras-ipo-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECerebras%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-competition-sambanova-groq-cerebras-show-faster-inference-speed-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESambaNova%20Systems%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-competition-sambanova-groq-cerebras-show-faster-inference-speed-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Espeed%20is%20a%20competitive%3C%2Fa%3E%20advantage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20inference%20service%20was%20available%20for%20free%2C%20developers%20came%20out%20of%20the%20woodwork%2C%20he%20said%2C%20with%20projects%20that%20couldn't%20be%20successful%20on%20slower%20chips.%20With%20more%20speed%2C%20developers%20can%20send%20one%20request%20through%20multiple%20models%20and%20use%20another%20model%20to%20choose%20the%20best%20response%20%E2%80%94%20all%20in%20the%20time%20it%20would%20usually%20take%20to%20fulfill%20just%20one%20request.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERoughly%20652%2C000%20developers%20are%20now%20using%20Groq%20API%20keys%2C%20Heaps%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHeaps%20expects%20speed%20to%20hook%20developers%20on%20Groq.%20But%20its%20novel%20plan%20for%20programming%20its%20chips%20gives%20the%20company%20a%20unique%20approach%20to%20the%20most%20crucial%20element%20within%20Nvidia's%20%26quot%3Bmoat.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f27acbca-49df-4ab4-a847-11d997565278%5C%22%3ENo%20need%20for%20CUDA%20libraries%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEverybody%2C%20once%20they%20deployed%20models%2C%20was%20gonna%20need%20faster%20inference%20at%20a%20lower%20cost%2C%20and%20so%20that's%20what%20we%20focused%20on%2C%26quot%3B%20Heaps%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20where's%20the%20CUDA%20equivalent%3F%20It's%20all%20in-house.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20actually%20have%20more%20than%201800%20models%20built%20into%20our%20compiler.%20We%20use%20no%20kernels%2C%20and%20we%20don't%20need%20people%20to%20use%20CUDA%20libraries.%20So%20because%20of%20that%2C%20people%20can%20just%20start%20working%20with%20a%20model%20that's%20built-in%2C%26quot%3B%20Heaps%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETraining%2C%20he%20said%2C%20requires%20more%20customization%20at%20the%20chip%20level.%20In%20inference%2C%20Groq's%20task%20is%20to%20choose%20the%20right%20models%20to%20offer%20customers%20and%20ensure%20they%20run%20as%20fast%20as%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20you're%20seeing%20with%20this%20massive%20swell%20of%20developers%20who%20are%20building%20AI%20applications%20%E2%80%94%20they%20don't%20want%20to%20program%20at%20the%20chip%20level%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20strategy%20comes%20with%20some%20level%20of%20risk.%20Groq%20is%20unlikely%20to%20accumulate%20a%20stable%20of%20developers%20who%20continuously%20troubleshoot%20and%20improve%20its%20base%20software%20like%20CUDA%20has.%20Its%20offering%20may%20be%20more%20like%20a%20restaurant%20menu%20than%20a%20grocery%20store.%20But%20this%20also%20means%20the%20barrier%20to%20entry%20for%20Groq%20users%20is%20the%20same%20as%20any%20other%20cloud%20provider%20and%20potentially%20lower%20than%20that%20of%20other%20chips.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20Groq%20started%20out%20as%20a%20company%20with%20a%20novel%20chip%20design%2C%20today%2C%20of%20the%20company's%20roughly%20300%20employees%2C%2060%25%20are%20software%20engineers%2C%20Heaps%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20us%20right%20now%2C%20there%20is%20a%20billions%20and%20billions%20of%20dollars%20industry%20emerging%2C%20that%20we%20can%20go%20capture%20a%20big%20share%20of%20market%20in%2C%20while%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20we%20continue%20to%20mature%20the%20compiler%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20being%20realistic%20about%20the%20near-term%2C%20Groq%20has%20lofty%20ambitions%2C%20which%20board%20CEO%20Jonathan%20Ross%20has%20described%20as%20%26quot%3Bproviding%20half%20the%20world's%20inference.%26quot%3B%20Ross%20also%20says%20the%20goal%20is%20to%20cast%20a%20net%20over%20the%20globe%20%E2%80%94%20to%20be%20achieved%20via%20joint%20ventures.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsaudi-arabia-ai-groq-a16z-vision-2030-mbs-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESaudi%20Arabia%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20on%20the%20way.%20Canada%20and%20Latin%20America%20are%20in%20the%20works.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjonathan-ross-groq-ai-power-list-2024%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERoss%20told%20BI%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20company%20also%20has%20a%20goal%20to%20ship%20108%2C000%20of%20its%20language%20processing%20units%20or%20LPUs%20by%20the%20first%20quarter%20of%20next%20year%20%E2%80%94%20and%202%20million%20chips%20by%20the%20end%20of%202025%2C%20most%20of%20which%20will%20be%20made%20available%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethrough%20its%20cloud.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20a%20tip%20or%20an%20insight%20to%20share%3F%20Contact%20Emma%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aecosgrove%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Eecosgrove%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20or%20use%20the%20secure%20messaging%20app%20Signal%3A%20443-333-9088%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2