2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20added%20in%20his%20post%20that%20the%20list%20of%20the%20Congress's%20%26quot%3Bsins%26quot%3B%20towards%20BR%20Ambedkar%20includes%3A%20%26quot%3Bgetting%20him%20defeated%20in%20elections%20not%20once%20but%20twice%2C%20Pandit%20Nehru%20campaigning%20against%20him%20and%20making%20his%20loss%20a%20prestige%20issue%2C%20denying%20him%20a%20Bharat%20Ratna%2C%20denying%20his%20portrait%20a%20place%20of%20pride%20in%20Parliament's%20Central%20Hall.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThe%20mask%20has%20fallen!%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnAs%20Parliament%20reflects%20on%2075%20glorious%20years%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20HM%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAmitShah%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40AmitShah%3C%2Fa%3E%20chose%20to%20TARNISH%20this%20occasion%20with%20DEROGATORY%20remarks%20against%20Dr.%20Babasaheb%20Ambedkar%2C%20that%20too%20in%20the%20temple%20of%20Democracy.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThis%20is%20a%20display%20of%20BJP's%20CASTEIST%20and%20ANTI-DALIT%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20(%40MamataOfficial)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMamataOfficial%2Fstatus%2F1869301392055370170%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%2018%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Trinamool%20chief%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20slammed%20the%20Home%20Minister%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Bmask%20has%20fallen%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%26quot%3BAs%20Parliament%20reflects%20on%2075%20glorious%20years%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20HM%20%40AmitShah%20chose%20to%20TARNISH%20this%20occasion%20with%20DEROGATORY%20remarks%20against%20Dr.%20Babasaheb%20Ambedkar%2C%20that%20too%20in%20the%20temple%20of%20Democracy.%20This%20is%20a%20display%20of%20BJP's%20casteist%20and%20anti-Dalit%20mindset.%20If%20this%20is%20how%20they%20behave%20after%20being%20reduced%20to%20240%20seats%2C%20imagine%20the%20damage%20they%20would've%20inflicted%20if%20their%20dream%20of%20400%20seats%20had%20been%20realised.%20They'd%20have%20rewritten%20history%20to%20entirely%20erase%20Dr.%20Ambedkar's%20contributions%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHM%20Amit%20Shah's%20remarks%20are%20an%20insult%20to%20the%20millions%20who%20look%20up%20to%20Babasaheb%20for%20guidance%20and%20inspiration.%20But%20what%20else%20can%20you%20expect%20from%20a%20party%20that%20has%20internalised%20hate%20and%20bigotry%3F%20Dr.%20Babasaheb%20Ambedkar%20is%20the%20Father%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20this%20outrageous%20remark%20is%20not%20only%20an%20outright%20attack%20on%20him%20but%20all%20members%20of%20the%20Drafting%20Committee%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20which%20symbolised%20India's%20unity%20in%20diversity%20with%20members%20from%20all%20castes%2C%20creeds%2C%20ethnicities%2C%20and%20religions%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Banerjee%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734515580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-09%2F3a59gsv_amit-shah-mamata-banerjee-2019-pti-650_650x400_19_September_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftrinamool-moves-privilege-notice-against-amit-shah-over-ambedkar-remarks-7276617%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amid%20the%20massive%20row%20over%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah's%20remarks%20on%20Dalit%20icon%20BR%20Ambedkar%2C%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20has%20moved%20a%20privilege%20notice%20against%20him%20and%20said%20he%20had%20undermined%20the%20legacy%20of%20the%20Constitution's%20architect%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftrinamool-moves-privilege-notice-against-amit-shah-over-ambedkar-remarks-7276617%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I'm%20a%20sexologist%2C%20bu