ent%2C%20making%20inflation%20stickier%2C%20further%20hindering%20their%20leeway%20to%20cut.%20Realizing%20this%2C%20the%20Fed%20would%20then%20need%20to%20push%20rate%20cuts%20out%20as%20it%20sought%20to%20justify%20them%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EColmar%20said%20the%20Fed%20would%20end%20up%20cutting%20by%2050-75%20basis%20points%20in%202024.%20The%20central%20bank%20has%20cut%20by%2075%20basis%20points%20so%20far%2C%20and%20is%20expected%20to%20drop%20them%20again%20in%20December%2C%20but%20the%20market%20at%20the%20time%20was%20pricing%20in%20more%20than%20an%2085%25%20chance%20that%20rates%20would%20be%20even%20lower%20by%20the%20end%20of%202024.%20Plus%2C%20rate%20cuts%20have%20come%20far%20later%20than%20the%20market%20originally%20expected.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20view%20was%20that%20interest%20rates%20weren't%20restrictive.%20Powell%20had%20just%20said%20that%20it%20was%20very%20restrictive%2C%20and%20we%20need%20to%20cut%20rates%20to%20bring%20it%20back%20down%20to%20equilibrium%20not%20to%20put%20us%20into%20recession.%20The%20market%20seemed%20to%20buy%20into%20that%2C%20and%20we%20said%2C%20'No%2C%20no%2C%20no%2C%20he's%20got%20it%20wrong.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202025%2C%20Colmar%20said%20he%20sees%20inflation%20hovering%20around%203%25%2C%20above%20the%20Fed's%202%25%20target.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f7816933-921d-4503-9668-baa024748768%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Small-cap%20explosion%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ESmall-cap%20explosion%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Small-cap%20explosion%5C%22%3EAfter%20lagging%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20for%20the%20first%20half%20of%20the%20year%2C%20small-cap%20stocks%20kicked%20off%20a%20furious%20rally%20in%20July%20as%20investors%20saw%20rate%20cuts%20on%20the%20horizon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220fd0e6b1-2cd3-425b-84a3-dfdd294ed867%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Jonathan%20Golub%2C%20chief%20US%20equity%20strategist%20at%20UBS%5C%22%3E%3Cstro