ls%2C%20technology%2C%20and%20utilities%20sectors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b934f0cc-043d-4b2b-9414-356cb64352c5%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Nvidia%20rally%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ENvidia%20rally%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Nvidia%20rally%5C%22%3ENvidia%20had%20an%20incredible%20year%20in%202023%2C%20and%20its%20share%20price%20only%20flew%20higher%20in%202024%2C%20rising%20180%25%20thanks%20to%20impressive%20earnings%20beats%20amid%20strong%20demand%20for%20its%20graphics%20processing%20unit%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b3323db0-9777-4009-ad77-8daa80a1df3e%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Matthew%20Ramsay%2C%20analyst%20at%20TD%20Cowen%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMatthew%20Ramsay%2C%20analyst%20at%20TD%20Cowen%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20December%20of%20last%20year%2C%20Nvidia%20was%20Ramsay's%20top%20chip%20stock%20pick%20for%202024.%20The%20stock%20had%20already%20appreciated%20220%25%20to%20a%20price%20of%20around%20%24500%2C%20and%20Ramsay%20was%20confident%20that%20it%20had%20another%2040%25%20upside%2C%20giving%20it%20a%20price%20target%20of%20%24700.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20year%20later%2C%20Nvidia%20has%20broken%20record%20after%20record%20and%20Ramsay%20has%20repeatedly%20raised%20his%20target.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20Nvidia's%2010-for-1%20stock%20split%20in%20June%2C%20Ramsay%20set%20the%20chip%20giant's%20price%20target%20to%20%24140%2C%20up%20from%20%24120%2C%20by%20year-end.%20Nvidia's%20flagship%20GPU%20product%20is%20used%20by%20every%20leading%20cloud%20service%20provider%20and%20AI%20company%20%E2%80%94%20including%20Google%2C%20Meta%2C%20Microsoft%2C%20Tesla%2C%20and%20OpenAI%20%E2%80%94%20to%20train%20their%20large%20language%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20suite%20of%20superior%20technology%2C%20long%20pedigree%20of%20innovation%2C%20and%20extensive%20growth-oriented%20investments%20should%20allow%20for%20strong%2C%20sustained%2C%20above-peer%20growth%20across%20a%20widening%20set%20of%20verticals%2C%26quot%3B%20Ramsay%20wrote%20in%20a%20June%209%20client%20note.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Nvidia%20GPUs%20are%20most%20well%20known%20for%20their%20use%20in%20data%20centers%2C%20Ramsay%20also%20mentioned%20a%20promising%20up-and-coming%20business%20line%3A%20autonomous%20driving%2C%20which%20became%20a%20billion-dollar%20component%20of%20Nvidia's%20business%20at%20the%20end%20of%20fiscal%20year%202024.%20Other%20growing%20end%20markets%20for%20Nvidia%20chips%20include%20gaming%2C%20healthcare%2C%20and%20robotics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENvidia%20has%20smashed%20analyst%20estimates%20every%20quarter%20this%20year%2C%20most%20recently%20posting%20%2435%20billion%20in%20revenues%20last%20month%20for%20fiscal%20year%202025%20Q3.%20TD%20Cowen%20has%20now%20upped%20Nvidia's%20price%20target%20to%20%24175%20for%20the%20next%2012%20months%2C%20citing%20sustained%20customer%20demand%20for%20the%20company's%20new%20Blackwell%20chips%2C%20released%20in%20March%20of%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERamsay%20recently%20left%20TD%20Cowen%2C%20the%20firm%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ae92a5c6-d3b8-4782-9f4e-8217ad0e8b75%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Gold%20surge%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EGold%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Esurge%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Gold%20surge%5C%22%3EThe%20price%20of%20gold%20also%20went%20on%20a%20tear%20this%20year%2C%20beating%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20so%20far%20thanks%20partly%20to%20rate%20cuts%20and%20global%20central%20banks%20buying%20up%20the%20asset.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c2ef6a04-8a0b-4ef8-a8d9-292b4b63df85%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22George%20Milling-Stanley%2C%20chief%20gold%20strategist%20at%20State%20Street%20Global%20Advisors%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EGeorge%20Milling-Stanley%2C%20chief%20gold%20strategist%20at%20State%20Street%20Global%20Advisors%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20headshot%20of%20George%20Milling-Stanley%2C%20chief%20gold