year%20for%20a%20price%20of%20%242%2C721%20per%20ounce%2C%20in%20line%20with%20Milling-Stanley's%20prediction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20potential%20of%20several%20inflationary%20policies%20being%20implemented%20under%20Trump%2C%20Milling-Stanley%20doesn't%20see%20demand%20for%20gold%20going%20anywhere%20in%20the%20year%20ahead.%20Tariffs%2C%20tax%20cuts%2C%20and%20increased%20government%20spending%20are%20all%20inflationary%20policies%20that%20will%20heat%20up%20the%20economy%20and%20increase%20prices%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20increasing%20national%20debt%20will%20be%20another%20factor%20supporting%20the%20price%20of%20gold%20as%20the%20dollar%20weakens%2C%20Milling-Stanley%20said.%20He%20predicts%20an%2080%25%20probability%20for%20the%20price%20of%20gold%20to%20stay%20at%20current%20levels%20or%20go%20higher%20%E2%80%94%20potentially%20as%20high%20as%20%243%2C100%20an%20ounce%20by%20the%20end%20of%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftop-market-forecasts-predictions-for-2025-oracles-of-wall-street-2024-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734514202000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67619bdad610a4acda56af9c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftop-market-forecasts-predictions-for-2025-oracles-of-wall-street-2024-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20many%20ways%2C%202024%20seemed%20like%20a%20continuation%20of%202023%20when%20it%20came%20to%20markets.%20But%20that%20doesn't%20mean%20trends%20were%20particularly%20easy%20to%20predict.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22wedwards%40businessinsider.com%20(William%20Edwards%2CChristine%20Ji)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A18%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftop-market-forecasts-predictions-for-2025-oracles-of-wall-street-2024-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A