%3E'%20to%20raise%20awareness%20and%20prevent%20similar%20incidents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20my%20story%20can%20in%20any%20way%20help%20prevent%20this%20from%20happening%20to%20at%20least%20just%20one%20woman%20or%20girl%2C%20then%20it%20was%20all%20worth%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2024%2F12%2F17%2Fus-news%2Ffemale-athlete-permanently-hurt-by-trans-athlete-speaks-out%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20New%20York%20Post%3C%2Fa%3E%20quoted%20McNabb%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%2017%2C%20McNabb%20was%20struck%20by%20a%20spiked%20ball%20during%20a%20high%20school%20match%2C%20an%20event%20that%20not%20only%20ended%20her%20athletic%20ambitions%20but%20reshaped%20the%20national%20conversation%20around%20fairness%20and%20safety%20in%20female%20sports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20game%20in%202022%2C%20McNabb%20and%20her%20teammates%20from%20a%20North%20Carolina%20school%20had%20concerns%20about%20competing%20against%20a%20team%20with%20a%20transgender%20player%20but%20felt%20silenced.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20never%20thought%20we%20would%20ever%20be%20put%20in%20this%20position%20to%20begin%20with.%20I%20didn't%20know%20one%20person%20who%20agreed%20with%20(a%20transgender%20athlete%20competing%20against%20us)%20on%20my%20team%2C%20but%20we%20didn't%20know%20what%20to%20do%2C%E2%80%9D%20McNabb%20told%20The%20New%20York%20Post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20game%20seemed%20routine%20until%20the%20opposing%20transgender%20player%20spiked%20the%20ball%20into%20McNabb's%20head%2C%20leaving%20her%20unconscious%20for%2030%20seconds.%20McNabb%20was%20rushed%20off%20the%20court%2C%20leaving%20her%20team%20to%20continue%20the%20match.%20The%20injuries%20she%20sustained%20%E2%80%94%20a%20concussion%2C%20neck%20damage%20and%20two%20black%20eyes%20%E2%80%94%20were%20just%20the%20beginning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20weeks%20that%20followed%2C%20McNabb%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20a%20traumatic%20brain%20injury%2C%20a%20brain%20bleed%2C%20partial%20paralysis%20and%20loss%20of%20peripheral%20vision%20on%20her%20right%20side.%20Cognitive%20impairments%20such%20as%20memory%20loss%20and%20confusion%2C%20coupled%20with%20severe%20headaches%2C%20have%20become%20a%20constant%20struggle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20100%20per%20cent%C2%A0avoidable%20if%20only%20my%20rights%20as%20a%20female%20athlete%20had%20been%20more%20important%20than%20a%20man's%20feelings%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20mother%2C%20Pamela%20McNabb%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20guilt%20Payton's%20father%20and%20I%20carry%20is%20heavy.%20At%20the%20time%20we%20weren't%20allowed%20to%20speak%20up.%20We%20couldn't%20say%2C%20%E2%80%98No%2C%20she's%20not%20playing%20against%20a%20boy%2C%20it's%20dangerous'.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMcNabb%20was%20forced%20to%20sit%20out%20the%20remainder%20of%20her%20senior%20volleyball%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20April%202023%2C%20McNabb%20testified%20before%20the%20North%20Carolina%20General%20Assembly%20in%20support%20of%20the%20Fairness%20in%20Women's%20Sports%20Bill%2C%20sharing%20her%20story%20to%20advocate%20for%20legislation%20banning%20transgender%20athletes%20from%20competing%20in%20women's%20sports.%20Soon%2C%20legislation%20was%20passed%20that%20prohibits%20transgender%20athletes%20from%20competing%20in%20women's%20sports%20at%20the%20middle%20school%2C%20high%20school%2C%20and%20collegiate%20levels%20in%20North%20Carolina.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20transgender%20athlete%20involved%20in%20the%20incident%20never%20apologised%20but%20once%20sent%20McNabb%20an%20Instagram%20message%2C%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CWow%20I%20really%20am%20living%20rent-free%20in%20your%20head%2C%20aren't%20I%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20these%20challenges%2C%20McNabb%20remains%20undeterred%20in%20her%20advocacy.%20%E2%80%9Cit%20doesn't%20bother%20me%20because%20I%20know%20what%20I'm%20saying%