%20on%20sites%20including%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftarget-says-shopper-behavior-stretched-waiting-to-buy-deals-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ETarget%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20Country%20Living.%20Then%20the%20chatbot%20suggested%20generic%20favorites%20like%20a%20Stanley%20mug%20and%20a%20foot%20massager.%20But%20as%20I%20scrolled%2C%20it%20also%20dropped%20links%20directly%20to%20more%20esoteric%20gifts%2C%20including%20a%20mug%20with%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-ceos-want-to-be-my-friend-relationship-big-tech-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EDonald%20Trump%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20it.%20%26quot%3BYou%20are%20a%20really%2C%20really%20great%20mom%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20mug%20read.%20%26quot%3BOther%20moms%3F%20Losers%2C%20total%20disasters.%26quot%3B%20I%20hadn't%20given%20Perplexity%20any%20indication%20of%20political%20ideology%20among%20my%20family%2C%20but%20the%20bot%20seemed%20to%20think%20sipping%20from%20Trump's%20visage%20every%20morning%20was%20a%20gift%20any%20mother%20would%20love.%20Then%20it%20suggested%20I%20make%20a%20jar%20and%20stuff%20it%20with%20memories%20I've%20written%20down.%20A%20cute%20idea%2C%20but%20I%20did%20let%20Perplexity%20know%20that%20I'm%20in%20my%2030s%20%E2%80%94%20I%20don't%20think%20the%20made-at-home%20gift%20for%20mom%20is%20going%20to%20cut%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E'Tis%20the%20season%20to%20scramble%20and%20buy%20tons%20of%20stuff%20people%20don't%20need%20or%20really%20even%20want.%20At%20least%20that's%20how%20it%20can%20feel%20when%20trying%20to%20come%20up%20with%20gifts%20for%20family%20members%20who%20have%20everything%20already.%20Money%20has%20been%20forked%20over%20for%20restaurant%20gift%20cards%20that%20collect%20dust%20or%20slippers%20and%20scarves%20that%20pile%20up%3B%20trendy%20gadgets%20are%20often%20relegated%20to%20junk%20drawers%20by%20March.%20As%20artificial%20intelligence%20becomes%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchatgpt-christmas-gift-ideas-for-family-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Emore%20integrated%20into%20online%20shopping%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20this%20whole%20process%20%3Cem%3Eshould%3C%2Fem%3E%20get%20easier%20%E2%80%94%20if%20AI%20can%20come%20to%20understand%20the%20art%20behind%20giving%20a%20good%20gift.%20Shopping%20has%20become%20one%20of%20Perplexity's%20top%20search%20categories%20in%20the%20US%2C%20particularly%20around%20the%20holidays%2C%20Sara%20Platnick%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20Perplexity%2C%20tells%20me.%20While%20Platnick%20didn't%20comment%20directly%20on%20individual%20gift%20suggestions%20Perplexity's%20chatbots%20makes%2C%20she%20tells%20me%20that%20product%20listings%20provided%20in%20responses%20are%20determined%20by%20%26quot%3Bratings%20and%20its%20relevance%20to%20a%20user's%20request.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20are%20chatbots%20to%20consult%20for%20advice%20this%20holiday%20season%2C%20like%20Perplexity%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feverything-you-need-to-know-about-chat-gpt-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EChatGPT%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20but%20AI%20is%20increasingly%20seeping%20into%20the%20entire%20shopping%20experience.%20From%20customer-service%20chatbots%20handling%20online%20shopping%20woes%20to%20ads%20serving%20recommendations%20that%20follow%20you%20across%20the%20web%2C%20AI's%20presence%20has%20ramped%20up%20alongside%20the%20explosion%20of%20interest%20in%20generative%20AI.%20Earlier%20this%20year%2C%20Walmart%20unveiled%20generative-AI-powered%20search%20updates%20that%20allow%20people%20to%20search%20for%20things%20like%20%26quot%3Bfootball%20watch%20party%26quot%3B%20instead%20of%20looking%20for%20items%20like%20chips%20and%20salsa%20individually%3B%20Google%20can%20put%20clothes%20on%20virtual%20models%20in%20a%20range%20of%20sizes%20to%20give%20buyers%20a%20better%20idea%20of%20how%20they'll%20look.%20In%20a%20world%20with%20more%20options%20than%20ever%2C%20there's%20more%20help%20from%20AI%2C%20acting%20as%20robo-elves%20in%20a%20way%20%E2%80%94%20omnipresent%20and%20sometimes%20invisible%20as%20you%20shop%20across%20the%20web.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20the%20indecisive%20shopper%2C%20AI%20may%20be%20a%20silver%20bullet%20to%20choosing%20from%20hundreds%20of%20sweaters%20to%20buy%2C%20plucking%20the%20best%20one%20from%20obscurity%20and%20putting%20an%20end%20to%20endless%20scrolling%20%E2%80%94%20or%20it%20might%20help%20to%20serve%20up%20so%20many%20targeted%20ads%20that%20it%20leads%20people%20to%20overconsume.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEither%20way%2C%20AI%20has%20been%20completely%20changing%20the%20e-commerce%20game.%20%26quot%3BIt%20allows%20a%20company%20to%20be%20who%20the%20customer%20wants%20it%20to%20be%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Hala%20Nelson%2C%20a%20professor%20of%20mathematics%20at%20James%20Madison%20University.%20%26quot%3BYou%20cannot%20hire%20thousands%20of%20human%20assistants%20to%20assist%20each%20customer%2C%20but%20you%20can%20deploy%20thousands%20of%20AI%20assistants.%26quot%3B%20Specialization%20comes%20from%20using%20third-party%20data%20to%20track%20activity%20and%20preferences%20across%20the%20web.%20In%20a%20way%2C%20that's%20the%20personalized%20level%20of%20service%20high-end%20stores%20have%20always%20provided%20to%20elite%20shoppers.%20Now%2C%20instead%20of%20a%20consultation%2C%20the%20expertise%20is%20built%20on%20surveillance.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECompanies%20also%20use%20AI%20to%20forecast%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-shopping-ai-features-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eshopping%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20trends%20and%20manage%20inventory%2C%20which%20can%20help%20them%20prepare%20and%20keep%20items%20in%20stock%20for%20those%20last-minute%20shoppers.%20Merchants%20are%20constantly%20looking%20for%20AI%20to%20get%20them%20more%20%E2%80%94%20to%20bring%20more%20eyes%20to%20their%20websites%2C%20to%20get%20people%20to%20add%20more%20items%20to%20their%20carts%2C%20and%20ultimately%20to%20actually%20check%20out%20and%20empty%20their%20carts.%20In%20October%20and%20early%20November%2C%20digital%20retailers%20using%20AI%20tech%20and%20agents%20increased%20the%20average%20value%20of%20an%20order%20by%207%25%20when%20compared%20to%20sites%20that%20did%20not%20employ%20the%20technology%2C%20according%20to%20Salesforce%20data.%20The%20company%20predicted%20AI%20and%20shopping%20agents%20to%20influence%2019%25%20of%20orders%20during%20the%20week%20of%20cyber%20deals%20around%20Thanksgiving.%20And%20AI%20can%20help%20%26quot%3Blevel%20the%20playing%20field%20for%20small%20businesses%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Adam%20Nathan%2C%20the%20founder%20and%20CEO%20of%20Blaze%2C%20an%20AI%20marketing%20tool%20for%20small%20businesses%20and%20entrepreneurs.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BThey%20don't%20want%20to%20necessarily%20be%20Amazon%2C%20Apple%2C%20or%20Nike%2C%20they%20just%20want%20to%20be%20the%20No.%201%20provider%20of%20their%20service%20or%20product%20in%20their%20local%20community%2C%26quot%3B%20Nathan%20says.%20%26quot%3BThey're%20not%20worried%20about%20AI%20taking%20their%20job%20%E2%80%94%20they're%20worried%20about%20a%20competitor%20using%20AI.%20They%20see%20it%20as%20basically%20a%20way%20to%20get%20ahead.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAI%20early%20adopters%20in%20the%20e-commerce%20space%20benefited%20last%20holiday%20season%2C%20but%20the%20tech%20has%20become%20even%20more%20common%20this%20year%2C%20says%20Guillaume%20Luccisano%2C%20the%20founder%20and%20CEO%20of%20Yuma%20AI%2C%20a%20company%20that%20automates%20customer%20service%20for%20sellers%20that%20use%20Shopify.%20Some%20merchants%20that%20used%20Yuma%20AI%20during%20the%20Black%20Friday%20shopping%20craze%20automated%20more%20than%2060%25%20of%20their%20customer-support%20tickets%2C%20he%20says.%20While%20some%20people%20lament%20having%20to%20deal%20with%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcustomer-service-phone-calls-paid-status-symbol-luxury-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cu%3Ebot%20instead%20of%20a%20person%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20Luccisano%20says%20the%20tech%20is%20getting%20better%2C%20and%20people%20are%20mostly%20concerned%20about%20whether%20their%20problem%20is%20getting%20solved%2C%20not%20whether%20the%20email%20came%20from%20a%20real%20person%20or%20generative%20AI.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20my%20ordeal%20with%20Perplexity%2C%20I%20turned%20to%20see%20how%20ChatGPT%20would%20fare%20in%20helping%20me%20find%20gifts%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20my%20family.%20For%20my%2011-year-old%20cousin%2C%20it%20suggested%20a%20Fitbit%20or%20smartwatch%20for%20kids%20to%20help%20her%20%26quot%3Bstay%20active.%26quot%3B%20A%20watch%20that%20tracks%20activity%20isn't%20something%20I%20feel%20comfortable%20giving%20a%20preteen%2C%20so%20I%20provided%20some%20more%20details.%20I%20told%20ChatGPT%20she%20loved%20the%20%26quot%3BTwilight%26quot%3B%20series%2C%20so%20it%20suggested%20a%20T-shirt%20with%20the%20Cullen%20family%20crest%20and%20a%20%26quot%3BTwilight%26quot%3B-themed%20journal%20to%20write%20fan%20fiction.%20It%20told%20me%20I%20could%20likely%20find%20these%20items%20on%20Etsy%20but%20it%20didn't%20give%20me%20direct%20links.%20(As%20her%20cool%20millennial%20cousin%20who%20has%20lived%20to%20tell%20of%20my%20own%20%26quot%3BTwilight%26quot%3B%20phase%20in%202007%2C%20I%20did%20end%20up%20buying%20a%20makeup%20bag%20from%20Etsy%20with%20a%20movie%20scene%20printed%20on%20it.)%20I%20also%20asked%20ChatGPT%20for%20suggestions%20for%20my%2085-year-old%20grandpa%2C%20and%20it%20came%20up%20with%20information%20about%20electronic%20picture%20frames%20%E2%80%94%20but%20the%20bulk%20of%20our%20family%20photos%20are%20stuffed%20in%20albums%20and%20shoeboxes%20in%20his%20closet%20and%20not%20easily%20digitized.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20could%20navigate%20this%20list%20because%20these%20are%20deep%20contextual%20things%20that%20I%20know%20about%20my%20family%20members%2C%20something%20AI%20doesn't%20know%20yet.%20Many%20of%20the%20best%20gifts%20I've%20ever%20received%20are%20from%20friends%20and%20family%20members%20who%20stumbled%20upon%20something%20they%20knew%20I%20would%20love%20%E2%80%94%20a%20vinyl%20record%20tucked%20in%20a%20bin%20or%20a%20print%20from%20an%20independent%20artist%20on%20display%20at%20a%20craft%20show.%20AI%20can%20play%20a%20role%20in%20helping%20people%20discover%20new%20items%20they%20may%20never%20have%20known%20to%20buy%20online%2C%20but%20it%20can't%20replace%20that%20intuition%20we%20have%20when%20we%20find%20the%20perfect%20thing%20for%20a%20loved%20one.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20still%20really%20wrestling%20with%3A%20How%20accurate%20is%20it%3F%20How%20much%20of%20a%20black%20box%20is%20it%3F%26quot%3B%20says%20Koen%20Pauwels%2C%20a%20professor%20of%20marketing%20at%20Northeastern%20University.%20%26quot%3BHumans%20are%20way%20better%20still%20in%20getting%20cues%20from%20their%20environment%20and%20knowing%20the%20context.%26quot%3B%20If%20you%20want%20to%20give%20a%20gift%20that's%20really%20a%20hit%2C%20it%20looks%20like%20you'll%20still%20have%20to%20give%20the%20AI%20elves%20a%20helping%20hand.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Famanda-hoover%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3EAmanda%20Hoover%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20is%20a%20senior%20correspondent%20at%20Business%20Insider%20covering%20the%20tech%20industry.%20She%2