the%20time%20a%20seller%20hires%20a%20real-estate%20agent%2C%20there's%20a%20good%20chance%20they've%20already%20consulted%20the%20digital%20oracle.%20For%20anyone%20with%20even%20a%20passing%20interest%20in%20the%20housing%20market%2C%20the%20Zestimate%20is%20a%20breezy%20way%20to%20take%20the%20temperature.%20Keep%20tabs%20on%20mortgage%20rates%20all%20you%20want%2C%20but%20they%20can't%20tell%20you%20that%20your%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbaby-boomers-housing-wealth-home-prices-housing-shortage-retirement-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20house%20has%20appreciated%2020%25%20over%20the%20past%20year%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20that%20your%20annoying%20coworker's%20property%20is%20worth%20more%20than%20yours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20industry%20insiders%2C%20however%2C%20regard%20the%20number%20as%20a%20starting%20point%20at%20best%20and%20dangerously%20misguided%20at%20worst.%20Real-estate%20agents%20recount%20arguments%20with%20sellers%20who%20reject%20their%20pricing%20advice%2C%20choosing%20instead%20to%20take%20the%20Zestimate%20as%20the%20word%20of%20God.%20One%20meme%20likens%20its%20disciples%20to%20adults%20who%20still%20believe%20in%20Santa.%20Zillow%20itself%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftimeline-of-how-zillow-stopped-buying-homes-over-two-weeks-2021-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elost%20hundreds%20of%20millions%20of%20dollars%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20the%20pandemic%20when%20it%20relied%20on%20its%20algorithm%20to%20buy%20homes%20at%20what%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20inflated%20prices%2C%20part%20of%20an%20ill-fated%20attempt%20to%20flip%20homes%20at%20scale.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Zestimate%20is%20just%20one%20of%20a%20slew%20of%20automated%20valuation%20models%20that%20are%20increasingly%20used%20by%20banks%2C%20investors%2C%20and%20laypeople%20to%20estimate%20the%20value%20of%20homes.%20No%20other%20model%2C%20however%2C%20has%20wormed%20its%20way%20into%20our%20culture%20like%20the%20Zestimate.%20The%20model%2C%20like%20other%20consumer-facing%20AVMs%2C%20is%20prone%20to%20errors%20that%20render%20it%20more%20of%20an%20amusement%20than%20a%20serious%20pricing%20tool.%20But%20while%20the%20algo's%20price-guessing%20skills%20may%20be%20suspect%2C%20it's%20undeniably%20elite%20at%20one%20thing%3A%20luring%20people%20to%20Zillow-dot-com.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Zestimate%20is%20both%20everywhere%20and%20an%20enigma.%20About%20104%20million%20homes%2C%20or%2071%25%20of%20the%20US%20housing%20stock%2C%20have%20a%20little%20dollar%20figure%20hovering%20above%20them%20on%20Zillow's%20website.%20One%20of%20them%20is%20the%20house%20in%20Austin%20where%20I%20was%20raised%20until%20the%20age%20of%2010.%20It's%20not%20for%20sale%2C%20but%20right%20underneath%20the%20address%2C%20in%20bold%2C%20is%20the%20Zestimate.%20Next%20to%20it%20is%20a%20%26quot%3BRent%20Zestimate%2C%26quot%3B%20or%20the%20amount%20the%20owner%20could%20probably%20charge%20a%20tenant%20each%20month.%20You%20can%20click%20to%20see%20a%20graph%20of%20its%20Zestimate%20over%20the%20past%20decade%20%E2%80%94%20the%20Zillow-fied%20value%20of%20my%20childhood%20home%20rose%20a%20staggering%2072%25%20from%20May%202020%20to%20its%20peak%20in%20May%202022%20but%20has%20since%20dropped%2024%25%20from%20that%20top%20tick%20thanks%20to%20the%20chill%20running%20through%20the%20Austin%20market.%20In%20just%20the%20past%2030%20days%2C%20the%20Zestimate%20has%20dropped%20by%20%244%2C455.%20Ouch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20how%20accurate%20are%20those%20numbers%2C%20though%3F%20Until%20the%20house%20actually%20trades%20hands%2C%20it's%20impossible%20to%20say.%20Zillow's%20own%20explanation%20of%20the%20methodology%2C%20and%20its%20outcomes%2C%20can%20be%20misleading.%20The%20model%2C%20the%20company%20says%2C%20is%20based%20on%20thousands%20of%20data%20points%20from%20public%20sources%20like%20county%20records%2C%20tax%20documents%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freal-estate-fight-clear-cooperation-realtors-zillow-pocket-listings-homes-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emultiple%20listing%20services%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20local%20databases%20used%20by%20real-estate%20agents%20where%20most%20homes%20are%20advertised%20for%20sale.%20Zillow's%20formula%20also%20incorporates%20user-submitted%20info%3A%20If%20you%20get%20a%20fancy%20new%20kitchen%2C%20for%20example%2C%20your%20Zestimate%20might%20see%20a%20nice%20bump%20if%20you%20let%20the%20company%20know.%20Zillow%20makes%20sure%20to%20note%20that%20the%20Zestimate%20can't%20replace%20an%20actual%20appraisal%2C%20but%20articles%20on%20its%20website%20also%20hail%20the%20tool%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bpowerful%20starting%20point%20in%20determining%20a%20home's%20value%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bgenerally%20quite%20accurate.%26quot%3B%20The%20median%20error%20rate%20for%20on-market%20homes%20is%20just%202.4%25%2C%20per%20the%20company's%20website%2C%20while%20the%20median%20error%20rate%20for%20off-market%20homes%20is%207.49%25.%20Not%20bad%2C%20you%20might%20think.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20that's%20where%20things%20get%20sticky.%20By%20definition%2C%20half%20of%20homes%20sell%20within%20the%20median%20error%20rate%2C%20e.g.%2C%20within%202.4%25%20of%20the%20Zestimate%20in%20either%20direction%20for%20on-market%20homes.%20But%20the%20other%20half%20don't%2C%20and%20Zillow%20doesn't%20offer%20many%20details%20on%20how%20bad%20those%20misses%20are.%20And%20while%20the%20Zestimate%20is%20appealing%20because%20it%20attempts%20to%20measure%20what%20a%20house%20is%20worth%20even%20when%20it's%20%3Cem%3Enot%3C%2Fem%3E%20for%20sale%2C%20it%20becomes%20much%20more%20accurate%20when%20a%20house%20actually%20hits%20the%20market.%20That's%20because%20it's%20leaning%20on%20actual%20humans%2C%20not%20computers%2C%20to%20do%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20grunt%20work.%20When%20somebody%20lists%20their%20house%20for%20sale%2C%20the%20Zestimate%20will%20adjust%20to%20include%20all%20the%20new%20seller-provided%20info%3A%20new%20photos%2C%20details%20on%20recent%20renovations%2C%20and%2C%20most%20importantly%2C%20the%20list%20price.%20The%20Zestimate%20keeps%20adjusting%20until%20the%20house%20actually%20sells.%20At%20that%20point%2C%20the%20difference%20between%20the%20sale%20price%20and%20the%20latest%20Zestimate%20is%20used%20to%20calculate%20the%20on-market%20error%20rate%2C%20which%2C%20again%2C%20is%20pretty%20good%3A%20In%20Austin%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20a%20little%20more%20than%2094%25%20of%20on-market%20homes%20end%20up%20selling%20for%20within%2010%25%20of%20the%20last%20Zestimate%20before%20the%20deal%20goes%20through.%20But%20Zillow%20also%20keeps%20a%20second%20Zestimate%20humming%20in%20the%20background%2C%20one%20that%20never%20sees%20the%20light%20of%20day.%20This%20version%20doesn't%20factor%20in%20the%20list%20price%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20carrying%20on%20as%20if%20the%20house%20never%20went%20up%20for%20sale%20at%20all.%20Instead%2C%20it's%20used%20to%20calculate%20the%20%26quot%3Boff-market%26quot%3B%20error%20rate.%20When%20the%20house%20sells%2C%20the%20difference%20between%20the%20final%20price%20and%20this%20shadow%20algorithm%20reveals%20an%20error%20rate%20that's%20much%20less%20satisfactory%3A%20In%20Austin%2C%20only%20about%2066%25%20of%20these%20%26quot%3Boff-market%20Zestimates%26quot%3B%20come%20within%2010%25%20of%20the%20actual%20sale%20price.%20In%20Atlanta%2C%20it's%2065%25%3B%20Chicago%2C%2058%25%3B%20Nashville%2C%2063%25%3B%20Seattle%2C%2069%25.%20At%20today's%20median%20home%20price%20of%20%24420%2C000%2C%20a%2010%25%20error%20would%20mean%20a%20difference%20of%20more%20than%20%2440%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWithout%20sellers%20spoonfeeding%20Zillow%20the%20most%20crucial%20piece%20of%20information%20%E2%80%94%20the%20list%20price%20%E2%80%94%20the%20Zestimate%20is%20hamstrung.%20It's%20a%20lot%20easier%20to%20estimate%20what%20a%20home%20will%20sell%20for%20once%20the%20sellers%20broadcast%2C%20%26quot%3BHey%2C%20this%20is%20the%20price%20we're%20trying%20to%20sell%20for.%26quot%3B%20Because%20the%20vast%20majority%20of%20sellers%20work%20with%20an%20agent%2C%20the%20list%20price%20is%20also%20usually%20based%20on%20that%20agent's%20knowledge%20of%20the%20local%20market%2C%20the%20finer%20details%20of%20the%20house%2C%20and%20comparable%20sales%20in%20the%20area.%20This%20September%2C%20per%20Zillow's%20own%20data%2C%20the%20typical%20home%20sold%20for%2099.8%25%20of%20the%20list%20price%20%E2%80%94%20almost%20exactly%20spot%20on.%20That%20may%20not%20always%20be%20the%20case%2C%20but%20the%20list%20price%20is%20generally%20a%20good%20indicator%20of%20the%20sale%20figure%20down%20the%20line.%20For%20a%20computer%20model%20of%20home%20prices%2C%20it's%20basically%20%3Cem%3Ethe%3C%2Fem%3E%20prized%20data%20point.%20In%20the%20world%20of%20AVMs%2C%20models%20that%20achieve%20success%20by%20fitting%20their%20results%20to%20list%20prices%20are%20deemed%20%26quot%3Bspringy%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bbouncy%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20like%20a%20ball%20tethered%20to%20a%20string%2C%20they%20won't%20stray%20too%20far.%20Several%20people%20I%20talked%20to%20for%20this%20story%20say%20they've%20seen%20this%20in%20action%20with%20Zillow's%20model%3A%20A%20seller%20lists%20a%20home%20and%20asks%20for%20a%20number%20significantly%20different%20from%20the%20Zestimate%2C%20and%20then%20watches%20as%20the%20Zestimate%20moves%20within%20a%20respectable%20distance%20of%20that%20list%20price%20anyway.%20Zillow%20itself%20makes%20no%20secret%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20it%20leans%20on%20the%20list%20price%20to%20arrive%20at%20its%20own%20estimate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20sites%20have%20their%20versions%20of%20the%20Zestimate%2C%20too%20%E2%80%94%20there%20are%20actually%20about%2025%20different%20AVMs%20in%20the%20market%2C%20says%20Lee%20Kennedy%2C%20the%20founder%20and%20managing%20director%20of%20AVMetrics%2C%20a%20company%20known%20for%20independently%20testing%20these%20models.%20Realtor.com%20will%20show%20you%20three%20estimates%2C%20each%20from%20a%20different%20AVM%20provider.%20Redfin%2C%20a%20Zillow%20competitor%2C%20also%20has%20its%20own%20model.%20Kennedy%20has%20been%20studying%20AVMs%20for%20more%20than%20three%20decades%2C%20but%20it%20wasn't%20until%20the%20advent%20of%20Zillow%20that%20the%20masses%20became%20aware%20of%20them.%20Consumer-facing%20AVMs%2C%20like%20the%20Zestimate%20or%20the%20Redfin%20Estimate%20(Restimate%3F)%20are%20meant%20to%20be%20used%20informally%2C%20he%20says%2C%20as%20casual%20starting%20points%20before%20consulting%20real%20experts.%20They're%20not%20supposed%20to%20be%20used%20for%20real%20pricing%2C%20which%20should%20be%20left%20to%20the%20big%20guys%20%E2%80%94%20the%20%26quot%3Bbusiness-to-business%26quot%3B%20AVMs%20used%20by%20banks%2C%20investors%2C%20and%20the%20government-sponsored%20enterprises%20Fannie%20Mae%20and%20Freddie%20Mac.%20Lauryn%20Dempsey%2C%20a%20real-estate%20agent%20in%20the%20Denver%20area%2C%20gives%20similar%20advice%20to%20her%20clients.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20tools%20that%20provide%20information%2C%26quot%3B%20Dempsey%20says%2C%20%26quot%3Bbut%20they%20should%20not%20be%20used%20in%20a%20vacuum%20to%20make%20decisions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22zillow%20home%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5fac0cf67f8f4200182a63db%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EZillow's%20own%20homebuying%20division%20lost%20millions%20of%20dollars%20thanks%20in%20part%20to%20using%20the%20Zestimate.%3Cp%3EJoe%20Raedle%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20business-to-business%20models%20are%20so%20costly%20to%20develop%2C%20Kennedy%20tells%20me%2C%20that%20they'll%20probably%20never%20be%20offered%20to%20regular%20people%20for%20free.%20But%20his%20testing%20indicates%20they're%20much%20more%20reliable.%20His%20firm%20has%20unveiled%20blind%20testing%20that%20looks%20at%20how%20models%20perform%20before%20taking%20into%20account%20the%20list%20price%2C%20a%20method%20that%20penalizes%20those%20aforementioned%20bouncy%20algorithms.%20The%20standard%20measurement%20breaks%20down%20how%20often%20the%20model%20can%20get%20within%2010%25%2C%20in%20either%20direction%2C%20of%20the%20actual%20selling%20price.%20In%20a%20highly%20urbanized%20area%20with%20lots%20of%20housing%20transactions%2C%20some%20of%20the%20models%20can%20correctly%20get%20close%20to%20the%20final%20selling%20price%20about%2080%25%20to%2090%25%20of%20the%20time%20%E2%80%94%20%26quot%3Bnot%20bad%2C%26quot%3B%20Kennedy%20says.%20AVMs%20of%20all%20kinds%20work%20best%20in%20areas%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20homes%20that%20look%20and%20feel%20roughly%20the%20same.%20Cookie-cutter%20suburbs%20are%20heaven%3B%20areas%20with%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20home%20styles%20and%20ages%2C%20like%20Boston%2C%20pose%20a%20greater%20challenge.%20The%20value%20of%20a%20ranch%20home%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20nowhere%20is%20even%20tougher%20to%20peg.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20the%20Zestimate%20isn't%20exactly%20unique%2C%20and%20it's%20far%20from%20the%20best.%20But%20to%20the%20average%20internet%20surfer%2C%20no%20AVM%20carries%20the%20weight%2C%20or%20swagger%2C%20of%20the%20original.%20To%20someone%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjonathan-miller-bio-appraiser-real-estate-data-expert-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJonathan%20Miller%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20president%20and%20CEO%20of%20the%20appraisal%20and%20consulting%20company%20Miller%20Samuel%2C%20the%20enduring%20appeal%20of%20the%20Zestimate%20is%20maddening.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20think%20of%20the%20Zestimate%2C%20for%20many%2C%20it%20gives%20a%20false%20anchor%20for%20what%20the%20value%20actually%20is%2C%26quot%3B%20Miller%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMiller%20is%20no%20unbiased%20observer.%20Given%20that%20he's%20an%20appraiser%20who%20estimates%20the%20value%20of%20homes%20for%20a%20living%2C%20it%20should%20come%20as%20no%20surprise%20that%20he's%20siding%20with%20the%20humans%20over%20the%20robots.%20But%20he%20raises%20real%20issues%2C%20highlighting%20the%20disconnect%20between%20the%20public's%20continued%20use%20of%20the%20Zestimate%20and%20its%20actual%20track%20record.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EI%20could%20say%20that%20I%20virtually%20stalked%20my%20childhood%20home%20for%20%26quot%3Bresearch%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20let's%20be%20real%3A%20By%20the%20time%20I%20scrolled%20to%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20page%2C%20I%20had%20fully%20surrendered%20to%20the%20voyeuristic%20urges%20that%20draw%20millions%20of%20visitors%20to%20the%20Zillow%20website%20each%20month.%20It's%20been%20almost%20two%20decades%20since%20I've%20stepped%20inside%20the%20house%2C%20and%20I%20can%20only%20imagine%20the%20changes%20its%20new%20owners%20have%20made%20to%20my%20old%20room%20(sadly%2C%20no%20pics%20of%20the%20interior).%20But%20with%20the%20aid%20of%20Zillow%2C%20my%20trip%20down%20memory%20lane%20was%20lined%20with%20data%3A%20I%20walked%20away%20with%20intimate%20knowledge%20of%20the%20home%20and%20its%20occupants.%20Prior%20to%202006%2C%20no%20regular%20person%20had%20this%20kind%20of%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20launch%20of%20Zillow%20spawned%20a%20whole%20genre%20of%20internet%20snooping%20that%2C%20if%20anything%2C%20has%20only%20intensified%20in%20the%20years%20since.%20When%20I%20call%20up%20John%20Wake%2C%20a%20former%20economist%20and%20real-estate%20agent%20who%20now%20writes%20the%20newsletter%20Real%20Estate%20Decoded%2C%20he%20reveals%20that%20he%2C%20too%2C%20looked%20up%20his%20childhood%20home%20only%20a%20few%20months%20ago.%20%26quot%3BThat%20part%20is%20really%20fun%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20tells%20me.%20Keeping%20tabs%20on%20your%20own%20Zestimate%2C%20though%2C%20can%20provide%20less%20of%20a%20thrill.%20In%20December%202022%2C%20after%20interest-rate%20hikes%20tamped%20down%20home%20prices%2C%20Wake%20shared%20with%20his%20followers%20on%20X%20that%20his%20Zestimate%20was%20down%2018%25%20from%20May%3A%20%26quot%3BYIKES!%26quot%3B%20In%20a%202020%20column%2C%20the%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%20editor%20Kris%20Frieswick%20opened%20up%20about%20the%20difficulty%20of%20quitting%20the%20algorithm%3A%20%26quot%3BMy%20self-worth%20is%20defined%20by%20my%20Zestimate.%20Each%20day%20I%20approach%20Zillow.com%20filled%20with%20hope%2C%20and%20fear.%26quot%3B%20The%20column%20reads%20mostly%20as%20tongue-in-cheek%2C%20but%20plenty%20of%20people%20take%20their%20number%20very%20seriously.%20As%20Frieswick%20pointed%20out%2C%20at%20least%20several%20disgruntled%20homeowners%20have%20actually%20sued%20Zillow%20over%20Zestimates%20they%20said%20were%20inaccurate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELooking%20up%20other%20people's%20houses%2C%20by%20comparison%2C%20is%20a%20mostly%20harmless%20pastime.%20Bosses%2C%20neighbors%2C%20lovers%2C%20and%20exes%20%E2%80%94%20all%20are%20fair%20game%20in%20the%20all-seeing%20eyes%20of%20the%20tool.%20During%20the%20heat%20of%20the%202021%20homebuying%20frenzy%2C%20a%20%26quot%3BSaturday%20Night%20Live%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fzillow-reinvented-as-erotic-voyeur-site-on-snl-1030051782%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esendup%20of%20a%20Zillow%20ad%3C%2Fa%3E%20declared%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20pleasure%20you%20once%20got%20from%20sex%20now%20comes%20from%20looking%20at%20other%20people's%20houses.%26quot%3B%20The%20skit%2C%20which%20featured%20a%20lot%20of%20moaning%20and%20sultry%20mood%20lighting%2C%20was%20mostly%20about%20the%20fantasies%20of%20browsing%20homes%20for%20sale%20on%20Zillow%20%E2%80%94%20as%20one%20YouTube%20commenter%20observed%2C%20%26quot%3BThey%20didn't%20even%20get%20into%20the%20naughty%20pleasure%20of%20looking%20up%20all%20your%20friends'%20Zestimate%20values.%26quot%3B%20This%20kicked%20off%20a%20thread%20of%20others%20chiming%20in%20with%20%26quot%3Bguilty!%26quot%3B%20and%20lots%20of%20cry-laughing%20emojis.%20%26quot%3BOMG%20I%20thought%20this%20was%20just%20my%20kink%2C%26quot%3B%20another%20person%20replied.%20I%20imagine%20all%20of%20these%20people%20at%20a%20raucous%20dinner%20party%2C%20bonding%20over%20their%20exploits%20on%20zillow.com.%20And%20here%20I%20am%2C%20the%20buzzkill%20in%20the%20corner%20talking%20about%20median%20error%20rates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EVirtual%20spelunking%20aside%2C%20the%20hazards%20of%20the%20Zestimate%20are%20most%20obvious%20when%20a%20seller%20actually%20decides%20to%20list%20their%20home.%20Francine%20Carstensen%2C%20a%20real-estate%20agent%20in%20Alabama%2C%20says%20those%20in%20her%20line%20of%20work%20have%20a%20complicated%20relationship%20with%20the%20Zestimate%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20love%20it%2C%20and%20we%20hate%20it.%26quot%3B%20A%20lofty%20estimate%20might%20jolt%20a%20homeowner%20into%20action%20%E2%80%94%20%26quot%3BI%20could%20sell%20my%20house%20for%20%3Cem%3Ewhat%3F!%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20drive%20more%20business%20her%20way.%20But%20the%20number%20can%20also%20make%20it%20hard%20to%20do%20her%20job.%20A%20few%20times%2C%20she%20tells%20me%2C%20she's%20lost%20clients%20over%20a%20pricing%20disagreement%20involving%20the%20Zestimate.%20It%20can%20be%20difficult%20enough%20to%20pry%20a%20seller%20away%20from%20their%20unrealistic%20expectations%20%3Cem%3Ewithout%20%3C%2Fem%3Ea%20number%20on%20a%20screen%20confirming%20their%20hopes%20for%20a%20bigger%20payday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20hate%20it%20when%20they%20tell%20me%2C%20'Well%2C%20this%20is%20what%20Zillow%20tells%20me%20my%20house%20is%20worth%2C'%26quot%3B%20Carstensen%20says.%20%26quot%3BBecause%20it's%20very%20rarely%20accurate.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccuracy%20may%20not%20even%20be%20the%20point.%20It%20didn't%20appear%20to%20be%20in%202006%2C%20when%20the%20beta%20version%20of%20the%20Zestimate%20launched.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Zestimate%20started%20out%20fairly%20inaccurate%2C%20but%20it%20didn't%20matter%2C%26quot%3B%20Rich%20Barton%2C%20a%20Zillow%20cofounder%20who%20was%20then%20its%20CEO%2C%20recalled%20in%20a%202021%20podcast%20episode.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20provocative.%26quot%3B%20Spencer%20Rascoff%2C%20another%20cofounder%20and%20former%20CEO%2C%20sold%20his%20own%20home%20in%202016%20for%2040%25%20less%20than%20its%20Zestimate.%20The%20next%20year%2C%20the%20company%20offered%20%241%20million%20to%20whoever%20could%20improve%20the%20Zestimate%20algorithm%20the%20most.%20The%20winning%20team%2C%20a%20group%20of%20three%20data%20scientists%20working%20remotely%20from%20the%20US%2C%20Canada%2C%20and%20Morocco%2C%20beat%20the%20Zillow%20benchmark%20by%2013%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENo%20misstep%20appeared%20more%20damning%2C%20however%2C%20than%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fzillow-homebuying-unit-shutting-down-layoffs-2021-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eimplosion%20of%20Zillow's%20homebuying%20business%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%202018%2C%20the%20company%20launched%20Zillow%20Offers%2C%20making%20all-cash%20offers%20to%20sellers%20looking%20to%20move%20quickly%20and%20seamlessly.%20In%20theory%2C%20Zillow%20could%20then%20turn%20around%20and%20offload%20the%20home%20in%20short%20order%20for%20a%20modest%20fee%2C%20plus%20however%20much%20the%20home%20had%20appreciated.%20The%20company%20used%20a%20combination%20of%20internal%20algorithms%20and%20human%20analysts%20to%20value%20the%20home%20and%20predict%20what%20it%20could%20sell%20for%20in%20a%20few%20months%20%E2%80%94%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20homeowners%20could%20get%20an%20immediate%20cash%20offer%20based%20on%20their%20Zestimate%20with%20just%20a%20few%20clicks.%20But%20the%20company's%20forecasts%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-is-zillow-buying-homes-ibuyer-impact-sellers-buyers-2021-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eturned%20out%20to%20be%20way%20off%20base%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Zillow%20Offers%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fzillow-ceo-explains-ibuying-shutdown-and-earnings-losses-2021-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esquandered%20%24422%20million%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20third%20quarter%20of%202021%20alone%20%E2%80%94%20a%20Business%20Insider%20investigation%20found%20that%20almost%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fzillow-offers-pause-ibuyers-homes-atlanta-phoenix-dallas-houston-minneapolis-2021-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etwo-thirds%20of%20the%20homes%20listed%20by%20Zillow%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Atlanta%2C%20Phoenix%2C%20Dallas%2C%20Houston%2C%20and%20Minneapolis%20were%20being%20marketed%20at%20a%20loss.%20Amanda%20Pendleton%2C%20a%20Zillow%20spokesperson%2C%20tells%20me%20it%20was%20the%20volatility%20of%20the%20market%2C%20not%20the%20Zestimate%2C%20that%20really%20led%20to%20the%20program's%20downfall.%20Once%20the%20losses%20came%20to%20light%2C%20the%20company%20swiftly%20shuttered%20the%20division%20and%20laid%20off%20a%20quarter%20of%20its%20staff.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20remember%20wondering%20whether%20this%20would%20be%20the%20death%20knell%20for%20the%20Zestimate%2C%20a%20kind%20of%20algorithm-has-no-clothes%20moment.%20I%20was%20wrong.%20Zillow%20and%20its%20best-known%20creation%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhome-trends-buyers-obsessed-with-in-2025-from-zillow-listings-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehaven't%20gone%20anywhere%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20the%20company%20continues%20to%20highlight%20its%20progress%2C%20providing%20periodic%20updates%20as%20its%20data%20scientists%20tinker%20away%20at%20the%20formulas.%20As%20search%20portals%20like%20Homes.com%20and%20Redfin%20jockey%20with%20Zillow%20for%20dominance%2C%20the%20Zestimate%20is%20too%20valuable%20of%20an%20asset%20to%20give%20up.%20People%20still%20flock%20to%20Zillow%20for%20those%20little%20numbers%20next%20to%20each%20home%2C%20for%20the%20thrill%20of%20feasting%20their%20eyes%20upon%20something%20that%2C%20%3Ca%20hre