Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fbroadcom-rises-as-top-ai-chip-supplier-after-nvidia-thanks-to-google-and-meta-partnerships-analyst-1033458720%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EASICs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20application-specific%20integrated%20circuits%20%E2%80%94%20an%20industry%20acronym%20meaning%20custom%20chips.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDesigners%20of%20custom%20AI%20chips%2C%20chief%20among%20them%20Broadcom%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fbroadcom-marvell-capitalize-on-generative-ai-demand-with-custom-asic-solutions-1033449187%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMarvell%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20are%20headed%20into%20a%20growth%20phase%2C%20according%20to%20Morgan%20Stanley.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229afb2732-f74d-4005-8bd2-196aa3da7498%5C%22%3ECustom%20chips%20are%20picking%20up%20speed%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20players%20in%20AI%20buy%20a%20lot%20of%20chips%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-stock-mystery-customer-microsoft-ubs-revenue-h100-gpu-chips-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENvidia%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20%243%20trillion%20giant%20with%20an%20estimated%2090%25%20of%20market%20share%20of%20advanced%20AI%20chips.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHeavily%20relying%20on%20one%20supplier%20isn't%20a%20comfortable%20position%20for%20any%20company%2C%20though%2C%20and%20many%20large%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faws-chips-supercomputer-ai-reinvent-big-tech-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENvidia%20customers%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20also%20developing%20their%20own%20chips.%20Most%20tech%20companies%20don't%20have%20large%20teams%20of%20silicon%20and%20hardware%20experts%20in%20house.%20Of%20the%20companies%20they%20might%20turn%20to%20design%20them%20a%20custom%20chip%2C%20Broadcom%20is%20the%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20multi-purpose%20chips%20like%20Nvidia's%20and%20AMD's%20graphics%20processing%20units%20are%20likely%20to%20maintain%20the%20largest%20share%20of%20the%20AI%20chip%20market%20in%20the%20long-term%2C%20custom%20chips%20are%20growing%20fast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMorgan%20Stanley%20analysts%20this%20week%20forecast%20the%20market%20for%20ASICs%20to%20nearly%20double%20to%20%2422%20billion%20next%20year.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMuch%20of%20that%20growth%20is%20attributable%20to%20Amazon%20Web%20Services'%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faws-exec-explains-why-nvidia-is-not-competitor-trainium-chip-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETrainium%3C%2Fa%3E%20AI%20chip%2C%20according%20to%20Morgan%20Stanley%20analysts.%20Then%20there%20are%20Google's%20in-house%20AI%20chips%2C%20known%20as%20TPUs%2C%20which%20Broadcom%20helps%20make.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20terms%20of%20actual%20value%20of%20chips%20in%20use%2C%20Amazon%20and%20Google%20dominate.%20But%20OpenAI%2C%20Apple%2C%20and%20TikTok%20parent%20company%20ByteDance%20are%20all%20reportedly%20developing%20chips%20with%20Broadcom%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cc27eb4e-d559-4ab1-be26-8e0acd889deb%5C%22%3EASICs%20bring%20bargaining%20power%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECustom%20chips%20can%20offer%20more%20value%2C%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20performance%20you%20get%20for%20the%20cost%2C%20according%20to%20Morgan%20Stanley's%20research.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EASICs%20can%20also%20be%20designed%20to%20perfectly%20match%20unique%20internal%20workloads%20for%20tech%20companies%2C%20accord%20to%20the%20bank's%20analysts.%20The%20better%20these%20custom%20chips%20get%2C%20the%20more%20bargaining%20power%20they%20may%20provide%20when%20tech%20companies%20are%20negotiating%20with%20Nvidia%20over%20buying%20GPUs.%20But%20this%20will%20take%20time%2C%20the%20analysts%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20Broadcom%2C%20Silicon%20Valley%20neighbor%20Marvell%20is%20making%20gains%20in%20the%20ASICs%20market%2C%20along%20with%20Asia-based%20players%20%3Cspan%3EAlchip%20Technologies%3C%2Fspan%3E%20and%20Mediatek%2C%20they%20added%20in%20a%20note%20to%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnalysts%20don't%20expect%20custom%20chips%20to%20ever%20fully%20replace%20Nvidia%20GPUs%2C%20but%20without%20them%2C%20cloud%20service%20providers%20like%20AWS%2C%20Microsoft%2C%20and%20Google%20would%20have%20much%20less%20bargaining%20power%20against%20Nvidia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOver%20the%20long%20term%2C%20if%20they%20execute%20well%2C%20cloud%20service%20providers%20may%20enjoy%20greater%20bargaining%20power%20in%20AI%20semi%20procurement%20with%20their%20own%20custom%20silicon%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Morgan%20Stanley%20analysts%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ea8fd853-8bb7-49fd-84d3-172cb2a107d4%5C%22%3ENvidia's%20big%20R%26amp%3BD%20budget%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20may%20not%20be%20all%20bad%20news%20for%20Nvidia.%20A%20%2422%20billion%20ASICs%20market%20is%20smaller%20than%20Nvidia's%20revenue%20for%20just%20one%20quarter.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENvidia's%20R%26amp%3BD%20budget%20is%20massive%2C%20and%20many%20analysts%20are%20confident%20in%20its%20ability%20to%20stay%20at%20the%20bleeding%20edge%20of%20AI%20computing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20as%20Nvidia%20rolls%20out%20new%2C%20more%20advanced%20GPUs%2C%20its%20older%20offerings%20get%20cheaper%20and%20potentially%20more%20competitive%20with%20ASICs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20believe%20the%20cadence%20of%20ASICs%20needs%20to%20accelerate%20to%20stay%20competitive%20to%20GPUs%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Morgan%20Stanley%20analysts%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20Broadcom%20and%20chip%20manufacturers%20on%20the%20supply%20chain%20rung%20beneath%2C%20such%20as%20TSMC%2C%20are%20likely%20to%20get%20a%20boost%20every%20time%20a%20giant%20cloud%20company%20orders%20up%20another%20custom%20AI%20chip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbroadcom-nvidia-custom-ai-chips-asics-2024-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22p