findia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fpassenger-dies-on-royal-caribbean-cruise-after-altercation-with-crew%2Farticleshow%2F116428755.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F116428755.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EA%2035-year-old%20father%2C%20Michael%20Virgil%2C%20died%20aboard%20a%20Royal%20Caribbean%20cruise%20after%20an%20alleged%20drunken%20rampage%20involving%20assaults%20on%20crew%20members%20and%20threats%20to%20passengers.%20Fellow%20travelers%20reported%20Virgil's%20violent%20behavior%2C%20which%20included%20kicking%20a%20crew%20member%20in%20the%20face%20and%20attempting%20to%20force%20his%20way%20into%20a%20locked%20closet.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fpassenger-dies-on-royal-caribbean-cruise-after-altercation-with-crew%2Farticleshow%2F116428755.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fpassenger-dies-on-royal-caribbean-cruise-after-altercation-with-crew%2Famp_articleshow%2F116428755.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fpassenger-dies-on-royal-caribbean-cruise-after-altercation-with-crew%2Famp_articleshow%2F116428755.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Explainer%3A%20Why%20Russia%20Wants%20To%20Capture%20Strategic%20Ukrainian%20City%20Of%20Pokrovsk%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ERussian%20forces%20are%20around%203%20kilometres%20(1.9%20miles)%20to%20the%20south%20of%20the%20strategically%20important%20eastern%20Ukrainian%20city%20of%20Pokrovsk%2C%20open%20source%20maps%20published%20by%20Russian%20and%20Ukrainian%20war%20bloggers%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20some%20key%20points%20about%20Pokrovsk%20and%20the%20battle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWHAT%20IS%20POKROVSK%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPokrovsk%20is%20a%20road%20and%20rail%20hub%20in%20Ukraine's%20eastern%20Donetsk%20region%2C%20which%20had%20a%20pre-war%20population%20of%20some%2060%2C000%20people.%20Ukraine%20estimates%20that%20around%2011%2C000%20of%20them%20remain%20in%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20lies%20on%20a%20key%20road%20used%20by%20the%20Ukrainian%20military%20to%20supply%20other%20embattled%20eastern%20outposts%20including%20the%20towns%20of%20Chasiv%20Yar%20and%20Kostiantynivka%20in%20the%20Donetsk%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUkraine's%20only%20mine%20that%20produces%20coking%20coal%20-%20used%20in%20its%20steel%20industry%20and%20vital%20for%20the%20country's%20pre-war%20economy%20-%20is%20just%20a%2020-minute%20drive%20to%20the%20west%20of%20Pokrovsk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20industry%20source%20said%20last%20week%20that%20Ukrainian%20steelmaker%20Metinvest%20BV%20had%20halted%20some%20of%20the%20mine's%20operations%20because%20of%20the%20proximity%20of%20advancing%20Russian%20troops.%20Its%20complete%20closure%20could%20more%20than%20halve%20Ukraine's%20steel%20output%2C%20the%20country's%20steelmakers'%20union%20has%20warned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPokrovsk%20has%20hosted%20since%202014%20an%20important%20technical%20university%2C%20the%20largest%20and%20oldest%20in%20the%20wider%20region.%20Damaged%20by%20shelling%2C%20it%20has%20now%20suspended%20its%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWHY%20DOES%20RUSSIA%20WANT%20POKROVSK%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoscow%20says%20it%20has%20annexed%20Ukraine's%20eastern%20Donetsk%20region%20and%20sees%20taking%20control%20of%20Pokrovsk%20as%20an%20important%20stepping%20stone%20to%20incorporating%20the%20entire%20region%20into%20Russia.%20Kyiv%20and%20the%20West%20reject%20Russia's%20territorial%20claims%20as%20illegal%20and%20accuse%20Moscow%20of%20prosecuting%20a%20war%20of%20colonial%20conquest.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EControl%20of%20the%20city%2C%20which%20the%20Russian%20media%20call%20%26quot%3Bthe%20gateway%20to%20Donetsk%26quot%3B%2C%20would%20allow%20Moscow%20to%20severely%20disrupt%20Ukrainian%20supply%20lines%20along%20the%20eastern%20front%20and%20boost%20its%20campaign%20to%20capture%20Chasiv%20Yar%2C%20which%20sits%20on%20higher%20ground%20offering%20potential%20control%20of%20a%20wider%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESqueezing%20the%20Ukrainian%20military's%20access%20to%20the%20road%20network%20in%20the%20vicinity%20would%20make%20it%20harder%20for%20Kyiv's%20troops%20to%20hold%20pockets%20of%20territory%20either%20side%20of%20Pokrovsk%2C%20which%20could%20allow%20Russia%20to%20consolidate%20and%20advance%20the%20front%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWHAT%20IS%20UKRAINE%20DOING%20TO%20DEFEND%20POKROVSK%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Ukrainian%20military%20official%20said%20on%20Saturday%20that%20Ukraine's%20military%20leadership%20had%20replaced%20the%20commander%20overseeing%20defences%20in%20the%20Donetsk%20region%20where%20Pokrovsk%20is%20located.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGeneral%20Oleksandr%20Lutsenko%2C%20the%20outgoing%20commander%2C%20had%20been%20criticised%20by%20Ukrainian%20military%20bloggers%20and%20some%20lawmakers%20for%20failing%20to%20stop%20Russian%20troops'%20relentless%20push%20towards%20Pokrovsk.%20He%20was%20replaced%20by%20General%20Oleksandr%20Tarnavskiy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOleksandr%20Syrskyi%2C%20Ukraine's%20top%20commander%2C%20has%20said%20his%20troops%20in%20and%20around%20Pokrovsk%20have%20prepared%20for%20the%20approaching%20Russians%20by%20repeatedly%20strengthening%20their%20defensive%20positions%20and%20he%20has%20spoken%20of%20sending%20new%20reserves%2C%20ammunition%20and%20equipment%20to%20bolster%20the%20defenders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERussian%20forces%20have%20taken%20villages%20and%20other%20settlements%20south%20of%20Pokrovsk%20in%20recent%20months%20and%20Ukraine%20says%20Moscow%20has%20been%20throwing%20everything%20it%20has%20at%20trying%20to%20break%20through%20while%20sustaining%20huge%20losses.%20Moscow%20says%20Ukrainian%20forces%20are%20taking%20serious%20losses.%20Neither%20side%20discloses%20full%20casualty%20figures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUkrainian%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelenskiy%20visited%20Pokrovsk%20in%20November%20where%20he%20spoke%20to%20troops%20defending%20the%20city%20and%20handed%20out%20military%20awards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWHAT%20DOES%20POKROVSK%20LOOK%20LIKE%20NOW%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20blue%20and%20yellow%20Ukrainian%20flag%20continues%20to%20fly%20over%20Pokrovsk%2C%20but%20the%20city%20is%20a%20shadow%20of%20its%20former%20self%2C%20with%20no%20electricity%2C%20gas%2C%20heating%20or%20piped%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReuters%20footage%20published%20on%20Dec%2013%20showed%20the%20facades%20of%20apartment%20blocks%20badly%20damaged%20and%20a%20few%20mostly%20elderly%20residents%20trudging%20through%20the%20streets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShell%20fire%20could%20be%20heard%20in%20the%20distance%2C%20%26quot%3Bdragon's%20teeth%26quot%3B%20anti-tank%20obstacles%20had%20been%20placed%20on%20some%20roads%2C%20and%20a%20small%20shop%20selling%20groceries%20was%20operating%20on%20a%20power%20generator.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734510600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fu6qifgao_russia-ukraine-war-_625x300_18_December_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Frussia-ukraine-war-explainer-why-russia-wants-to-capture-strategic-ukrainian-city-of-pokrovsk-7274661%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Russian%20forces%20are%20around%203%20kilometres%20(1.9%20miles)%20to%20the%20south%20of%20the%20strategically%20important%20eastern%20Ukrainian%20city%20of%20Pokrovsk%2C%20open-source%20maps%20published%20by%20Russian%20and%20Ukrainian%20war%2