ith%20Ashwin%20Retirement%20Timing.%20Says%2C%20%26quot%3BCould've...%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFormer%20Indian%20captain%20and%20legendary%20opener%20Sunil%20Gavaskar%20reacted%20to%20Ravichandran%20Ashwin's%20retirement%20decision's%20impact%20on%20the%20team%20and%20said%20the%20allrounder%20the%20same%20what%20Dhoni%20did%20during%202014-15%20Asutralia%20series.%20Ashwin%20announced%20his%20retirement%20from%20international%20cricket%20immediately%20following%20the%20drawn%20Gabba%20Test%20in%20the%20ongoing%20Border-Gavaskar%20Trophy.%20Gavaskar%20drew%20parallels%20to%20MS%20Dhoni's%20mid-series%20retirement%20during%20the%202014-15%20Test%20series%20in%20Australia%2C%20arguing%20that%20such%20decisions%20disrupt%20team%20planning.%20%26quot%3BHe%20could%20have%20said%2C%20listen%20after%20the%20end%20of%20the%20series%2C%20I%20won't%20be%20available%20for%20selection%20for%20India.%20What%20it%20does%20is%20that%2C%20similarly%20when%20MS%20Dhoni%20retired%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%203rd%20Test%20in%202014-15%20series%2C%20it%20leaves%20you%20one%20short%2C%26quot%3B%20Gavaskar%20told%20broadcasters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20selection%20committee%20has%20picked%20so%20many%20players%20for%20a%20tour%20with%20a%20purpose.%20If%20there%20are%20any%20injuries%20they%20can%20select%20from%20the%20reserve%20players%20to%20have%20in%20the%20team.%20So%2C%20Sydney%20is%20somewhere%20where%20there%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20support%20on%20offer%20for%20spinners.%20So%20India%20could%20have%20played%20with%20two%20spinners.%20You%20never%20know.%20He%20could%20have%20been%20there%20for%20sure.%20I%20don't%20know%20how%20the%20pitch%20in%20Melbourne%20will%20be%20like.%20Normally%2C%20you%20tend%20to%20look%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20series.%20That's%20it.%20In%20the%20middle%2C%20it%20is%20not%20usual%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20if%20Washington%20Sundar%20was%20being%20groomed%20to%20replace%20Ashwin%2C%20Gavaskar%20admitted%20it%20seemed%20likely.%20%26quot%3BMaybe%20Washington%20Sundar%20is%20ahead%20of%20him.%20Rohit%20mentioned%20that%20Sundar%20is%20flying%20out%20tomorrow.%20So%2C%20this%20marks%20the%20end%20of%20Ashwin%20as%20an%20international%20cricketer.%20He%20has%20been%20one%20heck%20of%20a%20cricketer%2C%26quot%3B%20Gavaskar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMenwahile%2C%20Sundar%20posted%20a%20heartfelt%20post%20for%20state-mate%20Ashwin%20on%20Instagram%2C%20following%20the%20allrounder's%20retirement.%20%26quot%3BMore%20than%20just%20a%20teammate%20-%20Ash%20anna%2C%20you%20have%20been%20an%20inspiration%2C%20a%20mentor%20and%20a%20true%20champion%20of%20the%20game.%20It's%20been%20an%20honour%20to%20share%20the%20field%20and%20the%20dressing%20room%20with%20you.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BComing%20from%20the%20same%20state%20of%20TN%2C%20I%20have%20grown%20up%20watching%20you%20from%20the%20close%20corners%20of%20Chepauk%20to%20playing%20against%20you%20and%20alongside%20you.%20Every%20moment%20has%20been%20a%20privilege.%20The%20learnings%2C%20both%20on%20and%20off%20the%20field%20are%20something%20I%20will%20carry%20with%20me%20forever.%20Wishing%20you%20success%20and%20happiness%20in%20whatever%20comes%20next%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20post%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAshwin's%20retirement%20comes%20at%20a%20crucial%20juncture%20in%20the%20Border-Gavaskar%20Trophy%2C%20with%20the%20series%20delicately%20poised%201-1%20with%20the%20drawn%20Gabba%20Test.%20His%20absence%20leaves%20a%20gap%20in%20India's%20bowling%20arsenal%2C%20especially%20as%20they%20prepare%20for%20the%20upcoming%20Test%20in%20Melbourne%20and%20Sydney%2C%20traditionally%20a%20spinner-friendly%20venue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734509880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F