0of%20the%20Allu%20Arjun%20case%20have%20opened%20the%20door%20for%20accusations%20ranging%20from%20%E2%80%9Ctargeting%20the%20actor%E2%80%9D%20to%20%E2%80%9Cauthoritarian%20handling%20of%20the%20issue.%E2%80%9D%20Reddy%20%E2%80%93%20who%20also%20serves%20as%20the%20home%20minister%20%E2%80%93%20has%20categorically%20backed%20the%20charges%20against%20Allu%20Arjun.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20charges%20include%20Sections%20105%20and%20118(1)%20read%20with%20Section%203(5)%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Nyaya%20Sanhita%2C%20which%20correspond%20to%20culpable%20homicide%20not%20amounting%20to%20murder%2C%20a%20crime%20punishable%20by%205-10%20years%20imprisonment%2C%20and%20a%20fine.%20One%20of%20the%20sections%20also%20pertains%20to%20voluntarily%20causing%20hurt%20with%20dangerous%20weapons%20or%20means%2C%20punishable%20by%20up%20to%20three%20years%20imprisonment%20or%20a%20fine.%20The%20crux%20of%20the%20matter%20is%20that%20Allu%20Arjun%20allegedly%20caused%20the%20stampede%20at%20the%20Sandhya%20Theatre%20in%20Hyderabad%20on%20December%205%2C%20which%20led%20to%20the%20death%20of%20a%2035-year-old%20woman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EGovernment%20Overreach%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20important%20to%20make%20a%20clear%20distinction%20here.%20The%20issue%20isn't%20holding%20the%20star%20accountable%2C%20but%20rather%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20charges%20and%20statements%E2%80%94vilifying%20the%20actor%20as%20having%20intentionally%20caused%20grievous%20harm%20and%20loss%20of%20life%E2%80%94that%20has%20led%20to%20accusations%20of%20an%20%E2%80%9Coverreach%E2%80%9D%20by%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReddy's%20aggressive%20defence%20of%20the%20case%2C%20including%20his%20statement%20that%20Allu%20Arjun%20is%20a%20relative%20of%20his%20and%20the%20remark%20that%20the%20actor%20was%20irresponsible%2C%20reveals%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20personal%20stance%20on%20the%20incident.%20The%20argument%20that%20%E2%80%9Call%20are%20equal%20before%20the%20law%E2%80%9D%20is%20a%20compelling%20one.%20But%20there's%20much%20more%20to%20this%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police's%20argument%20is%20that%20despite%20the%20jurisdictional%20police%20inspector%20advising%20Sandhya%20Theatre%E2%80%94%C2%A0through%20a%20handwritten%20communication%E2%80%94that%20chaos%20would%20ensue%20if%20the%20stars%20of%20%3Cem%3EPushpa%202%3C%2Fem%3E%20appeared%20at%20the%20venue%2C%20Allu%20Arjun%20still%20came%20and%20emerged%20from%20the%20sunroof%20of%20his%20car%2C%20%E2%80%9Cinstigating%E2%80%9D%20the%20chaos%20that%20led%20to%20death%20and%20injury.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20victims%20were%20fans%20of%20Allu%20Arjun%20who%20had%20come%20to%20watch%20the%20screening%20of%20his%20film.%20Unfortunately%2C%20this%20is%20not%20the%20first%20casualty%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Cfirst-day%2C%20first-show%E2%80%9D%20fan%20frenzy%2C%20a%20frequent%20occurrence%20in%20Telugu%2C%20Tamil%2C%20and%20Kannada%20cinema.%20While%20fan%20frenzy%20around%20film%20and%20political%20personalities%20is%20common%20(figures%20like%20SRK%20and%20Salman%20Khan%20deal%20with%20it)%2C%20the%20scale%20of%20it%20in%20the%20South%2C%20particularly%20in%20Telugu%2C%20Tamil%2C%20and%20Kannada%20cinema%2C%20is%20much%20bigger%20(though%20it%20is%20subdued%20in%20Malayalam%20cinema).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20that%20the%20huge%20crowds%20and%20frenzy%20were%20anticipated%2C%20could%20Allu%20Arjun%20have%20been%20more%20circumspect%20and%20refrained%20from%20adding%20to%20it%20by%20arriving%20at%20the%20theatre%20and%20waving%20to%20the%20crowd%3F%20Yes%2C%20he%20should%20have%20been%20more%20responsible.%20But%20so%20should%20every%20star%20and%20politician%20in%20discouraging%20fan%20frenzy%20and%20educating%20people%20against%20such%20madness.%20Do%20they%3F%20The%20answer%20is%20a%20resounding%20no%2C%20because%20most%20thrive%20on%20it.%20Some%20have%20spoken%20out%20against%20it%2C%20but%20most%20enjoy%20the%20ego%20boost%20it%20provides.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Weak%20Case%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20indeed%20a%20moral%20responsibility%20for%20celebrities%2C%20but%20the%20core%20question%20here%20is%3A%20does%20it%20make%20Allu%20Arjun%20a%20criminal%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirstly%2C%20it's%20unclear%20if%20the%20organisers%20informed%20him%20of%20the%20advice%20from%20the%20police.%20Secondly%2C%20the%20police%20and%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20could%20have%20taken%20preventive%20action%20and%20been%20more%20forceful%20in%20advising%20the%20star%20not%20to%20attend%20the%20first-day%2C%20first-show%20screening.%20Had%20they%20done%20so%20and%20he%20disobeyed%2C%20they%20might%20have%20a%20stronger%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20enforcement%20of%20their%20advice%20and%20preventive%20actions%20also%20falls%20under%20the%20police's%20responsibility.%20What%20did%20they%20do%20after%20advising%E2%80%94if%20indeed%20they%20did%E2%80%94Sandhya%20Theatre%20against%20having%20Allu%20Arjun%20attend%20the%20screening%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20also%20shows%20that%20the%20administration%20had%20prior%20knowledge%20of%20what%20was%20planned.%20Given%20that%20such%20frenzy%20is%20the%20rule%20and%20not%20the%20exception%2C%20was%20enough%20done%20to%20prevent%20it%3F%20More%20importantly%2C%20has%20enough%20been%20done%20to%20prevent%20it%20in%20the%20future%3F%20If%20not%2C%20wouldn't%20that%20also%20make%20the%20head%20of%20the%20police%20force%20and%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20accountable%3F%20It%20seemed%20like%20a%20knee-jerk%20reaction%20from%20Reddy%20and%20his%20police%20administration.%20The%20entire%20incident%20may%20diminish%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20political%20capital.%20Allu%20Arjun%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20comes%20across%20as%20someone%20who%20remained%20gracious%20in%20the%20face%20of%20adversity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20Bears%20Responsibility%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20have%20been%20deaths%20at%20funerals%2C%20political%20rallies%2C%20and%20religious%20gatherings.%20Reddy%20has%20witnessed%20this%20in%20his%20political%20career%2C%20including%20at%20some%20of%20his%20rallies.%20How%20often%20have%20the%20personalities%20involved%20been%20booked%3F%20SRK%20was%20booked%20once%20for%20a%20stampede%20at%20the%20Vadodara%20railway%20station%2C%20but%20the%20Gujarat%20High%20Court%20quashed%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20hindsight%2C%20the%20police%20and%20Sandhya%20Theatre%20management%20bear%20the%20primary%20legal%20responsibility.%20However%2C%20it's%20not%20easy%20to%20blame%20them%20alone%2C%20as%20society%20as%20a%20whole%20must%20take%20responsibility%20for%20fan%20frenzy%20as%20a%20social%20ill.%20It%20is%20irrational%20and%20needs%20to%20be%20addressed.%20Stars%20have%20a%20role%20in%20dissuading%20it%2C%20but%20everyone%20else%20needs%20to%20share%20the%20responsibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStrict%20action%20is%20necessary%20to%20set%20a%20precedent%20and%20ensure%20such%20incidents%20don't%20happen%20again.%20However%2C%20the%20government's%20approach%2C%20which%20has%20been%20described%20as%20%E2%80%9Cexcessive%E2%80%9D%20by%20several%20legal%20experts%2C%20has%20only%20led%20to%20an%20embarrassment%20for%20itself.%20And%20Revanth%20Reddy%20seems%20to%20have%20shot%20himself%20in%20the%20foot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(TM%20Veeraraghav%20is%20Executive%20Editor%2C%20NDTV)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734509460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fgd423iro_allu-arjun-news_625x300_14_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Frevanth-reddy-has-shot-himself-in-the-foot-with-allu-arjun-case-7275961%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20governments%20approach%2C%20which%20has%20been%20described%20as%20%26quot%3Bexcessive%26quot%3B%20by%20several%20legal%20experts%2C%20has%20only%20l