show%2F116427728.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BAmbedkar%20No%20Less%20Than%20God%26quot%3B%3A%20Opposition%20Slams%20Amit%20Shah's%20%26quot%3BFashion%26quot%3B%20Remark%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20massive%20political%20row%20has%20erupted%20over%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah's%20remarks%20on%20BR%20Ambedkar%20during%20his%20address%20to%20Rajya%20Sabha%20yesterday.%20While%20the%20Congress%20has%20accused%20Mr%20Shah%20of%20insulting%20the%20architect%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20alleged%20that%20the%20Opposition%20party%20was%20circulating%20clipped%20videos%20and%20playing%20cheap%20tricks.%20At%20Parliament%20this%20morning%2C%20Opposition%20MPs%20held%20photos%20of%20BR%20Ambedkar%20and%20raised%20slogans%20demanding%20the%20Home%20Minister's%20apology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20the%20House%20during%20the%20debate%20to%20mark%2075%20years%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20Mr%20Shah%20said%20taking%20BR%20Ambedkar's%20name%20had%20become%20a%20%26quot%3Bfashion%26quot%3B%20now.%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3EAbhi%20ek%20fashion%20ho%20gaya%20hai%20-%20Ambedkar%2C%20Ambedkar%2C%20Ambedkar%2C%20Ambedkar%2C%20Ambedkar%2C%20Ambedkar.%20Itna%20naam%20agar%20bhagwan%20ka%20lete%20to%20saat%20janmon%20tak%20swarg%20mil%20jata%3C%2Fem%3E%20(It%20has%20become%20a%20fashion%20to%20say%20Ambedkar%2C%20Ambedkar%2C%20Ambedkar%2C%20Ambedkar%2C%20Ambedkar%2C%20Ambedkar'.%20If%20they%20took%20God's%20name%20so%20many%20times%2C%20they%20would%20have%20got%20a%20place%20in%20heaven)%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Home%20Minister%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BTake%20his%20name%20100%20times%20more%2C%20but%20I%20want%20to%20say%20what%20are%20your%20sentiments%20about%20him.%26quot%3B%20He%20said%20BR%20Ambedkar%20had%20to%20resign%20from%20the%20first%20Cabinet%20following%20his%20disagreement%20with%20the%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru-led%20government.%20%26quot%3BAmbedkar%20ji%20has%20said%20several%20times%20that%20he%20was%20not%20satisfied%20with%20the%20treatment%20of%20Scheduled%20Castes%20and%20Scheduled%20Tribes%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20BR%20Ambedkar%20was%20also%20unhappy%20with%20the%20government's%20policy%20approach%20and%20its%20stand%20on%20Article%20370.%20%26quot%3BHe%20wanted%20to%20quit%20(the%20cabinet)%2C%20he%20was%20given%20an%20assurance%2C%20and%20when%20the%20assurance%20was%20not%20fulfilled%2C%20he%20resigned%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Shah%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Home%20Minister's%20remarks%20drew%20a%20scathing%20criticism%20from%20the%20Congress.%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20said%20in%20a%20veiled%20swipe%2C%20%26quot%3BThose%20following%20Manusmriti%20would%20naturally%20be%20troubled%20by%20Ambedkar.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20said%20Mr%20Shah's%20%26quot%3Binsult%26quot%3B%20of%20BR%20Ambedkar%20has%20again%20proved%20that%20the%20BJP%20and%20its%20ideological%20parent%20RSS%20were%20%26quot%3Bagainst%20the%20Tricolour%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bopposed%20the%20Ashok%20Chakra%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20wanted%20to%20implement%20Manusmriti%20instead%20of%20the%20Constitution.%20Babasaheb%20Ambedkar%20did%20not%20let%20this%20happen%2C%20that's%20why%20they%20hate%20him%20so%20much.%20The%20Modi%20government's%20ministers%20must%20understand%20that%20for%20crores%20of%20people%20like%20me%2C%20Babasaheb%20is%20no%20less%20than%20God.%20He%20is%20a%20messiah%20for%20Dalits%2C%20tribals%2C%20backward%2C%20minorities%20and%20the%20poor.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20will%20be%20raising%20this%20issue%20in%20Parliament%20today.%20Party%20MP%20B%20Manickam%20Tagore%20has%20decided%20to%20move%20an%20adjournment%20motion%20seeking%20a%20discussion%20on%20this%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDuring%20the%20discussion%20on%20the%2075th%20anniversary%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20the%20Home%20Minister%20cynically%20dismissed%20the%20importance%20of%20Dr.%20Ambedkar%2C%20stating%20that%20it%20has%20become%20a%20'fashion'%20for%20the%20Congress%20Party%20to%20repeatedly%20take%20his%20name%2C%20comparing%20it%20to%20the%20invocation%20of%20God's%20name.%20He%20further%20trivialised%20Dr.%20Ambedkar's%20monumental%20contribution%20by%20suggesting%20that%20those%20who%20invoke%20his%20name%20as%20frequently%20as%20the%20Congress%20does%20would%20attain%20%26quot%3Bswarg%26quot%3B%20(heaven).%20This%20blasphemous%20statement%20is%20an%20attempt%20to%20undermine%20Dr.%20Ambedkar's%20pivotal%20role%20in%20drafting%20the%20Indian%20Constitution%2C%20which%20guarantees%20equality%2C%20justice%2C%20and%20dignity%20for%20all%20citizens%2C%20especially%20the%20marginalized%20communities%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Tagore%20has%20said.%20Speaking%20to%20NDTV%2C%20the%20Congress%20MP%20said%20the%20Home%20Minister%20must%20apologise%20to%20the%20nation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20a%20video%20of%20a%20section%20of%20Mr%20Shah's%20speech%2C%20Congress%20spokesperson%20Supriya%20Shrinate%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BOnly%20a%20man%20who%20detests%20the%20Constitution%20can%20insult%20Babasaheb.%20Why%20do%20Sangh%20people%20hate%20Babasaheb's%20name%20so%20much%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20trashed%20the%20Congress's%20charge.%20Parliamentary%20Affairs%20Minister%20Kiren%20Rijiju%20has%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20%26quot%3BAgain%20a%20cheap%20trick%20of%20the%20Congress%20Party.%20Home%20Minister%20AmitShah%20Ji%20was%20referring%20to%20how%20Congress%20kept%20misusing%20Dr%20B.R.%20Ambedkar's%20name%20but%20insulted%20him%20and%20never%20followed%20his%20ideals.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20Ms%20Shrinate's%20post%2C%20BJP%20spokesperson%20Pradeep%20Bhandari%20called%20her%20a%20%26quot%3Bfake%20news%20factory%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BAmitShah%20ji%20was%20exposing%20your%20party%20-%20Cong