%20during%20the%20Covid-19%20pandemic.%20The%20authors%20are%20spot-on%20when%20they%20observe%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20new%20plan%20of%20benevolent%20statesmanship%20linked%20with%20nationalism%20has%20now%20become%20an%20inevitable%20part%20of%20politics%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%20own%20take%20is%20that%20while%20the%202024%20verdict%20leaned%20more%20toward%20benevolent%20statesmanship%2C%20the%20element%20of%20macho%20nationalism%20was%20somewhat%20missing.%20It%20seemed%20like%20a%20collection%20of%20several%20state%20elections.%20While%20West%20Bengal%20voted%20one%20way%2C%20neighbouring%20Bihar%20went%20the%20opposite.%20The%20verdict%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20was%20full%20of%20surprises%2C%20and%20the%20people%20of%20Maharashtra%2C%20Jharkhand%2C%20and%20Rajasthan%20chose%20to%20punish%20some%20and%20reward%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20theme%20that%20stood%20out%20was%20that%20people%20did%20not%20appreciate%20any%20political%20party%20taking%20them%20for%20granted.%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3ELogon%20ne%20aukat%20dikha%20di%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20(people%20showed%20a%20mirror%20to%20all)%2C%20as%20a%20friend%20said%20the%20day%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20results%20were%20announced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20book%20delves%20into%20the%20multiplicity%20of%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20verdict.%20Instead%20of%20a%20single%20meta-narrative%2C%20there%20were%20several%20at%20play%E2%80%94some%20cancelling%20each%20other%20out%2C%20and%20some%20reinforcing%20one%20another.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%20editor-in-chief%20beautifully%20captured%20the%20pattern%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Flok-sabha-election-verdict-2024-shows-politics-is-now-deeply-personal-for-indians-5857120%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20a%20multi-layered%20verdict%E2%80%94the%20beauty%20of%20the%20India%20we%20know%20and%20have%20grown%20up%20in.%20The%202024%20mandate%20is%20like%20a%20rainbow%20whose%20colours%20politicians%20will%20have%20t