ven%20capable%20of%20handling%20much%20of%20the%20work%20previously%20done%20by%20human%20employees.%20One%20of%20the%20most%20significant%20AI%20integrations%20includes%20an%20AI%20assistant%20powered%20by%20OpenAI%2C%20which%20has%20taken%20over%20the%20responsibilities%20of%20700%20customer%20service%20agents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20decrease%20in%20headcount%2C%20Mr%20Siemiatkowski%20assured%20existing%20employees%20the%20company%20would%20share%20the%20productivity%20gains%20from%20AI.%20%E2%80%9CWe're%20going%20to%20give%20some%20of%20the%20improvements%20that%20the%20efficiency%20that%20AI%20provides%20by%20increasing%20the%20pace%20at%20which%20the%20salaries%20of%20our%20employees%20increases%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20Bloomberg.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKlarna's%20shift%20toward%20automation%20is%20also%20linked%20to%20its%20plans%20for%20future%20growth.%20The%20company%20has%20confidentially%20submitted%20a%20draft%20registration%20statement%20for%20an%20initial%20public%20offering%20(IPO)%20and%20is%20looking%20to%20expand%20its%20US%20footprint.%20%E2%80%9CKlarna%20is%20a%20bank%20in%20Europe%2C%20we%20want%20to%20become%20a%20bank%20in%20the%20US%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20and%20is%20ready%20to%20take%20up%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20offer%20of%20fast-tracking%20banking%20licenses%20in%20exchange%20for%20a%20%241%20billion%20investment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Siemiatkowski%20said%20that%20AI%20has%20become%20integral%20to%20the%20company's%20operations%2C%20replacing%20traditional%20roles%20and%20driving%20productivity.%20This%2C%20however%2C%20has%20raised%20questions%20about%20the%20future%20of%20human%20jobs%2C%20with%20experts%20like%20McKinsey%20%26amp%3B%20Company%20warning%20that%20millions%20of%20workers%20could%20face%20job%20displacement%20due%20to%20AI%20advancements%20by%202030.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Klarna%20is%20not%20actively%20expanding%20its%20workforce%2C%20it%20continues%20to%20hire%20for%20essential%20roles%2C%20particularly%20in%20engineering.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20trend%20of%20AI%20replacing%20jobs%20is%20not%20unique%20to%20Klarna.%20IBM%2C%20another%20major%20tech%20company%2C%20has%20also%20signalled%20the%20potential%20for%20AI%20to%20replace%20up%20to%2030%20per%20cent%20of%20HR%20roles%20within%20the%20next%20five%20years%2C%20as%20CEO%20Arvind%20Krishna%20discussed%20in%20a%20recent%20Bloomberg%20interview.%20Earlier%2C%20Mr%20Krishna%20also%20implemented%20a%20new%20rule%20for%20managers%20saying%20they%20must%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fibm-chief-arvind-krishnas-rule-for-managers-move-near-office-or-leave-4958494%5C%22%3Eeither%20relocate%20near%20an%20office%20or%20leave%20the%20company%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734504300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fatkl31n_office-generic_625x300_21_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftech-giant-halts-human-hiring-ceo-claims-ai-can-replace-most-office-roles-7274933%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Klarna%2C%20a%20leading%20%26quot%3Bbuy%20now%2C%20pay%20later%26quot%3B%20fintech%20provider%2C%20has%20halted%20human%20hiring%20and%20relies%20on%20artificial%20intelligence%20(AI)%20to%20perform%20tasks%20once%20handled%20by%20hundreds%20of%20employees.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftech-giant-halts-human-hiring-ceo-claims-ai-can-replace-most-office-roles-7274933%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Russia%20detains%20Uzbek%20citizen%20'recruited%20by%20Ukraine'%20over%20killing%20of%20general%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734503940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F12%2F1920x1080%2Fskynews-russia-moscow-bomb_6778379.jpg%3F20241217065241%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Frussia-detains-uzbek-citizen-recru