.com%2F351304%2Fchennai-bengaluru-water-crisis-prashant-sharma-grey-water-recycling-in-schools%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egrassroots%20solutions%20to%20the%20water%20crisis%20and%20the%20floods%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20strategise%20their%20actions%20for%20these%20missions%2C%20the%20students%20rely%20on%20a%20design-thinking%20process%20called%20the%20%E2%80%98Problems%20to%20Projects%E2%80%99%20or%20%E2%80%98P2P%E2%80%99.%20This%20model%20equips%20the%20stakeholders%20(the%20students)%20with%20the%20skills%20and%20knowledge%20needed%20to%20tackle%20the%20issue.%20It%20has%20eight%20stages%3A%20gather%2C%20map%2C%20empathise%2C%20define%2C%20ideate%2C%20test%20and%20prototype%2C%20operations%2C%20and%20marketing%2Fshowcase%2Fevaluation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%202490px)%20100vw%2C%202490px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUlsoor2-1_11zon-1733754214.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222490%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20children%20have%20also%20launched%20weekly%20heritage%20walks%20around%20the%20city%2C%20held%20every%20Sunday%20and%20open%20to%20everyone.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUlsoor2-1_11zon-1733754214.jpg%202490w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUlsoor2-1_11zon-1733754214-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUlsoor2-1_11zon-1733754214-500x333.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUlsoor2-1_11zon-1733754214-768x512.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUlsoor2-1_11zon-1733754214-1536x1024.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUlsoor2-1_11zon-1733754214-2048x1365.jpg%202048w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUlsoor2-1_11zon-1733754214-1200x800.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUlsoor2-1_11zon-1733754214-150x100.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-387860%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221660%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20children%20have%20also%20launched%20weekly%20heritage%20walks%20around%20the%20city%2C%20held%20every%20Sunday%20and%20open%20to%20everyone.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20not%20a%20top-down%20approach.%20They%20arrive%20at%20things%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sreeja%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20take%20the%20first%20step%20to%20positively%20change%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F366063%2Fnehal-shah-travel-with-kids-children-nature-trails-treks-experiences-toddlers-mumbai%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20children%E2%80%99s%20worldview%20of%20their%20city%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20its%20calamities%2C%20they%20began%20with%20preschoolers%2C%20who%20were%20asked%20to%20let%20their%20thoughts%20about%20Bengaluru%20roam%20uncaged%20on%20a%20sheet%20of%20paper.%20The%20drawings%20were%20full%20of%20aversive%20thought%20bubbles%20like%2C%20%E2%80%9CGo%20away%2C%20says%20Bengaluru%E2%80%9D%2C%20%E2%80%9CPothole%20city!%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20%E2%80%9CToo%20many%20people%2C%20too%20much%20pollution%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20clear%20that%20the%20children%20only%20had%20a%20surface-level%20connection%20with%20their%20city%2C%20and%20that%20drove%20all%20the%20apathy.%20%E2%80%9CThat%20was%20not%20going%20to%20help%20them%20become%20change%20agents.%20Football%20ground%2C%20apartment%20park%2C%20apartment%20friends%2C%20and%20school%20%E2%80%94%20this%20was%20all%20they%20could%20imagine%20when%20they%20thought%20about%20Bengaluru.%E2%80%9D%20Sreeja%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESreeja%20and%20the%20team%20quickly%20decided%20to%20take%20them%20on%20trips%20around%20the%20city%2C%20which%20came%20to%20be%20known%20as%20%E2%80%98Child%20in%20the%20City%E2%80%99%20walks.%20The%20Unicorns%20also%20accompanied%20them.%20They%20were%20also%20taken%20to%20lakes%2C%20with%20Jakkur%20Lake%20being%20an%20often-visited%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20younger%20children%20worked%20on%20expanding%20their%20horizons%20about%20the%20city%2C%20Bengaluru%20was%20hit%20with%20a%20water%20crisis%2C%20with%20lake%20rejuvenation%20efforts%20already%20in%20the%20works.%20So%20the%20Unicorns%20made%20no%20ado%20in%20rushing%20to%20experts%20and%20stakeholders%20with%20their%20questions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBridging%20gaps%2C%20one%20conversation%20at%20a%20time%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20spoke%20to%20farmers%2C%20environmentalists%2C%20hydrologists%2C%20people%20at%20the%20Bangalore%20Development%20Authority%2C%20and%20local%20volunteers%20%E2%80%94%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20who%20were%20stakeholders%20in%20lake%20rejuvenation.%20We%20even%20interviewed%20the%20team%20at%20a%20sustainable%20design%20firm%20to%20understand%20the%20role%20that%20construction%20and%20urban%20planning%20have%20to%20play.%20We%20also%20studied%20the%20work%20done%20by%20Jala%20Poshan%2C%20a%20citizen%20participation%20programme%2C%20to%20rejuvenate%20Jakkur%20Lake%2C%20and%20we%20were%20so%20fascinated%20with%20the%20impact%20that%20common%20people%20can%20bring%20about%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mihika%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20insights%20from%20these%20conversations%20came%20together%2C%20with%20threads%20of%20information%20carefully%20untangled.%20Patterns%20were%20identified%2C%20and%20scripts%20were%20crafted.%20Armed%20with%20powerful%20messages%2C%20the%20students%20stepped%20out%20to%20give%20the%20lake%20a%20voice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20did%20a%20show%20for%20our%20annual%20day%20which%20was%20presented%20in%20Jakkur%20Lake%E2%80%99s%20own%20voice%20in%20the%20context%20of%20the%20water%20crisis%2C%20Jakkur%20being%20an%20example%20of%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20lakes.%20It%20was%20called%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EBengaluru%2C%20Once%20a%20City%20of%20Lakes%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%2C%20and%20we%20depicted%20the%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F345780%2Fbengaluru-water-crisis-rain-reach-programme-hariharan-chandrashekhar-helps-children-in-bbmp-schools-conserve-water%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20importance%20of%20lake%20rejuvenation%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20lakes%20in%20general%20for%20our%20city.%20We%20performed%20it%20at%20different%20places%20across%20the%20city.%20It%20even%20had%20a%20dance!%E2%80%9D%20Simran%2C%20a%20student%2C%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FIDcTO_M-nC0%3Fsi%3DYVWPVg-cGZph_EHo%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20impact%20of%20the%20work%20did%20not%20end%20there.%20It%20manifested%20again%20in%20the%20form%20of%20footfall%20for%20their%20Saturday%20morning%20awareness%20workshops%20and%20stalls.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20children%20have%20also%20launched%20weekly%20heritage%20walks%20around%20the%20city%2C%20held%20every%20Sunday%20and%20open%20to%20everyone.%20These%20walks%20offer%20a%20chance%20to%20rediscover%20Bengaluru%E2%80%99s%20hidden%20heritage%20through%20landmarks%20like%20Ulsoor%20Lake%2C%20Cubbon%20Park%2C%20and%20Nandi%20Durg.%20They%20have%20even%20prepared%20treasure%20cues%20to%20make%20the%20experience%20more%20engaging%2C%20and%20taken%20the%20lead%20in%20getting%20all%20this%20done%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sreeja%20says%20with%20a%20proud%20smile.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESparkling%20Mindz%20students%20were%20just%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20performing%20snippets%20of%20%3Cem%3EBengaluru%2C%20Once%20a%20City%20of%20Lakes%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20different%20corners%20of%20the%20city.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20like%20we%20were%20translating%20the%20lake%E2%80%99s%20emotions%20into%20human%20language%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sabreesh%2C%20another%20student%2C%20says.%20His%20benchmate%2C%20Nikhil%2C%20adds%20that%20they%20had%20even%20started%20work%20in%20the%20school%2C%20like%20creating%20recharge%20pits%20and%20making%20arrangements%20for%20water%20harvesting%2C%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20they%20were%20water-sufficient%20in%20the%20face%20of%20another%20water%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20who%20knew%20that%20not%20many%20months%20later%2C%20they%20would%20be%20listening%20to%20Mihika%20share%20her%20story%20about%20how%20floods%20in%20the%20city%20made%20her%20miss%20her%20Trinity%20exam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%202943px)%20100vw%2C%202943px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FTRUI-Team-1-1_11zon-1734349588.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222943%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sparkling%20Mindz%20students%20ready%20to%20host%20a%20waste%20managerment%20stall%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FTRUI-Team-1-1_11zon-1734349588.jpg%202943w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FTRUI-Team-1-1_11zon-1734349588-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FTRUI-Team-1-1_11zon-1734349588-500x375.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FTRUI-Team-1-1_11zon-1734349588-768x576.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FTRUI-Team-1-1_11zon-1734349588-1536x1152.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FTRUI-Team-1-1_11zon-1734349588-2048x1536.jpg%202048w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2