confidence%20to%20play%20the%20games%20on%20his%20own.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20time%2C%20through%20consistent%20practice%20and%20by%20making%20the%20experience%20interactive%2C%20he%20began%20to%20see%20remarkable%20improvements%20in%20the%20children%E2%80%99s%20ability%20to%20stay%20focused.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20key%20was%20to%20ensure%20the%20experience%20was%20fun%20and%20engaging%2C%20rather%20than%20just%20a%20routine%20task%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20biggest%20hurdles%2C%20however%2C%20was%20teaching%20the%20children%20the%20rules%20of%20the%20games.%20At%20first%2C%20the%20concept%20of%20scoring%20or%20tracking%20points%20was%20foreign%20to%20many.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20explained%20to%20a%20child%20that%20his%20score%20was%20adding%20up%20to%20something%20bigger%2C%20he%20began%20to%20grasp%20the%20concept%20and%20feel%20a%20sense%20of%20accomplishment%2C%E2%80%9D%20Siddhant%20says.%20With%20patience%2C%20encouragement%2C%20and%20positive%20reinforcement%2C%20the%20children%20gradually%20began%20to%20grasp%20the%20rules.%20As%20they%20progressed%2C%20they%20took%20pride%20in%20their%20newfound%20understanding%2C%20and%20with%20each%20small%20victory%2C%20their%20confidence%20grew.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20brother%2C%20Shaurya%2C%20was%20born%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F388365%2Fovercoming-down-syndrome-jijo-das-journey-to-becoming-ultraviolette-photographer%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDown%20syndrome%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20like%20to%20go%20out%20and%20play%20because%20children%20his%20age%20don%E2%80%99t%20include%20him.%20But%20with%20the%20Nintendo%20Wii%2C%20he%20can%20play%20whenever%20he%20wants.%20It%E2%80%99s%20made%20a%20huge%20difference%20in%20his%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Jhanvi%20Kuldeep%2C%20one%20of%20many%20individuals%20positively%20impacted%20by%20INTECH.