vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-3-1733814988.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rinchon%20with%20the%20Longpi%20jars%20containing%20soy%20wax%20candles.%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-3-1733814988.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-3-1733814988-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-3-1733814988-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-3-1733814988-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-3-1733814988-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-388009%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERinchon%20with%20the%20Longpi%20jars%20containing%20soy%20wax%20candles%3B%20Image%20courtesy%3A%20October%20Pumpkin%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoy%20wax%20candles%20burn%2050%20percent%20slower%20than%20paraffin%20wax%20candles%2C%20making%20them%20more%20cost-effective%20despite%20being%20slightly%20pricier.%20The%20soy%20wax%20used%20is%20sourced%20from%20Gujarat%2C%20where%20purified%20soybean%20oil%20undergoes%20hydrogenation%20%E2%80%94%20a%20process%20that%20introduces%20hydrogen%20to%20convert%20the%20liquid%20oil%20into%20solid%20wax.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMany%20candles%20in%20the%20Indian%20market%20suffer%20from%20%E2%80%98candle%20tunnelling%2C%E2%80%99%20where%20the%20wax%20burns%20unevenly%2C%20leaving%20a%20circular%20pit%20around%20the%20wick%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%20%E2%80%9COur%20candles%20are%20thoroughly%20tested%20to%20prevent%20this%20issue%2C%20and%20we%20also%20educate%20customers%20on%20proper%20burning%20techniques.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20our%20scents%20are%20crafted%20using%20fragrance%20oils%20that%20are%20rigorously%20tested%20and%20sourced%20from%20companies%20committed%20to%20using%20non-toxic%20chemicals%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%20%E2%80%9CThese%20oils%20are%20blended%20into%20the%20wax%20at%20a%20precise%20temperature.%20Each%20scent%20is%20designed%20to%20evoke%20specific%20emotions%20and%20experiences.%20For%20instance%2C%20some%20of%20our%20popular%20ones%20include%20%E2%80%98Forest%2C%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%98Walk%20Around%20the%20Bakery%2C%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98In%20the%20Library.%E2%80%99%E2%80%9D%20She%20adds%20with%20a%20smile%2C%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%98In%20the%20Library%E2%80%99%20even%20captures%20the%20nostalgic%20scent%20of%20old%20books!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F7A-kBnADm-8%3Ffeature%3Doembed%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%223%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22281%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20has%20faced%20challenges%20such%20as%20courier%20transportation%20glitches%20and%20packaging%20issues.%20They%20pack%20their%20candles%20in%20Longpi%20jars%20using%20eco-friendly%20materials%20like%20paper%20and%20cardboard%20boxes.%20Large%20Longpi%20jar%20candles%2C%20containing%20approximately%201%20kg%20of%20soy%20wax%2C%20are%20priced%20at%20around%20Rs%203%2C500.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOctober%20Pumpkin%20has%20also%20participated%20in%20two%20pop-up%20stalls%20at%20Nagaland%20House%2C%20New%20Delhi%2C%20under%20%E2%80%98Home%20%26amp%3B%20Heart%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20a%20collective%20of%20Northeast%20women%20entrepreneurs%20based%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E2.%20Zero-energy%20low-cost%20cold%20storage%20units%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFarmers%20in%20Meghalaya%E2%80%99s%20West%20Khasi%20Hills%20struggle%20with%20warehousing%2C%20storage%2C%20and%20logistics.%20The%20lack%20of%20affordable%2C%20energy-efficient%20storage%20solutions%20for%20fruits%20and%20vegetables%20often%20results%20in%20significant%20post-harvest%20losses%20and%20reduced%20incomes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20small%20project%20can%20make%20a%20big%20difference%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Binolin%20Syiemlieh%2C%20centre%20manager%20at%20the%20Nongstoin%20Social%20Service%20Society%20(NSSS)%2C%20the%20non-profit%20driving%20this%20innovation.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20set%20up%20simple%2C%20small-scale%2C%20zero-energy%20storage%20units%20near%20farmers%E2%80%99%20fields%20to%20preserve%20their%20produce.%20So%20far%2C%20three%20units%20have%20been%20constructed%20in%20different%20villages%2C%20each%20costing%20Rs%201.64%20lakh.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20NSSS%20works%20for%20the%20welfare%20of%20the%20community%20in%20several%20areas%20like%20farming%2C%20mental%20health%2C%20and%20child%20services.%20I%20am%20involved%20in%20projects%20for%20farmers.%20I%20mobilise%20farmers%20and%20also%20help%20them%20access%20assistance%20from%20government%20and%20private%20agencies%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20the%20idea%20for%20these%20storage%20units%20came%20from%20the%20farmers%20themselves.%20Struggling%20to%20store%20their%20produce%2C%20they%20faced%20losses%20even%20before%20reaching%20the%20markets%2C%20compounded%20by%20low%20prices.%20While%20the%20project%20began%20in%202019%2C%20its%20progress%20was%20delayed%20due%20to%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENSSS%20oversees%20the%20construction%20of%20these%20units%20by%20hiring%20contractors%2C%20using%20locally%20available%20materials%20like%20burned%20bricks%2C%20river%20sand%2C%20bamboo%20poles%2C%20CGI%20sheets%2C%20iron%20nails%2C%20cement%2C%20and%20pebbles.%20Each%20unit%20can%20store%20up%20to%20a%20tonne%20of%20produce%2C%20preserving%20it%20for%20one%20to%20four%20weeks.%20Remarkably%2C%20the%20units%20are%20quick%20to%20construct%20%E2%80%94%20taking%20just%20a%20day%20or%20two%20%E2%80%94%20and%20require%20no%20maintenance.%20Farmers%20can%20use%20them%20free%20of%20charge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20fill%20the%20gap%20between%20two%20layers%20of%20the%20structure%20with%20river%20sand%20and%20pebbles.%20This%20sand%20is%20watered%20twice%20a%20day.%20This%20keeps%20the%20produce%20cool.%20Each%20unit%20benefits%20over%20120%20farmers%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Binolin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-5-1733815262.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Binolin%20Syiemlieh%2C%20centre%20manager%20at%20the%20Nongstoin%20Social%20Service%20Society%20(NSSS)%2C%20says%20their%20non-profit%20has%20set%20up%20simple%2C%20small-scale%2C%20zero-energy%20storage%20units%20near%20farmers%E2%80%99%20fields%20to%20preserve%20their%20produce.%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-5-1733815262.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-5-1733815262-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-5-1733815262-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-5-1733815262-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-5-1733815262-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-388012%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EBinolin%20Syiemlieh%2C%20centre%20manager%20at%20the%20Nongstoin%20Social%20Service%20Society%20(NSSS)%2C%20says%20their%20non-profit%20has%20set%20up%20simple%2C%20small-scale%2C%20zero-energy%20storage%20units%20near%20farmers%E2%80%99%20fields%20to%20preserve%20their%20produce%3B%20Image%20courtesy%3A%20Nongstoin%20Social%20Service%20Society%20(NSSS)%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20cold%20storage%20units%2C%20though%20rooted%20in%20scientific%20principles%2C%20involve%20no%20elaborate%20technology.%20They%20are%20managed%20by%20the%20Village%20Executive%20Committee%20(VEC)%2C%20ensuring%20equitable%20access%20for%20all%20villagers%20while%20keeping%20produce%20clean%20and%20fresh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20project%20is%20funded%20by%20the%20Meghalaya%20Basin%20Management%20Agency%20(MBMA)%2C%20a%20not-for-profit%20organisation%20handling%20externally%20aided%20government%20projects.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20initiative%20is%20supported%20by%20the%20World%20Bank%20under%20an%20innovation%20fund%20that%20helps%20improve%20or%20scale%20up%20solutions.%20It%20is%20part%20of%20the%20Community-Led%20Landscape%20Management%20Project%2C%20which%20focuses%20on%20addressing%20natural%20resource%20management%20issues%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Wankit%20Swer%2C%20general%20manager%20at%20MBMA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20farmers%20are%20smallholders%20with%20limited%20production.%20After%20meeting%20their%20own%20needs%2C%20the%20excess%20is%20sold.%20Without%20proper%20storage%2C%20they%20often%20resort%20to%20distress%20sales%20of%20perishable%20items.%20These%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F314446%2Fchennai-student-eco-friendly-tech-increases-produce-shelf-life-sunharvested-coolrooms%2F%5C%22%3Ecold%20storage%20units%3C%2Fa%3E%20prevent%20such%20sales%20and%20provide%20a%20better%20solution%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E3.%20Anti-microbial%20fabric%20made%20from%20banana%20fibre%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENagaland-based%20venture%20Hengna%20%26amp%3B%20Maben%20Private%20Limited%20is%20making%20remarkable%20progress%20in%20harnessing%20banana%20fibre.%20%E2%80%9COur%20banana%20fibre%20project%20is%20part%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98Runway%20India%E2%80%99%20division%20of%20our%20company%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Major%20Tanay%20Maben%2C%20co-founder%20of%20the%20venture.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20currently%20in%20the%20research%20and%20development%20(R%26amp%3BD)%20phase%2C%20working%20on%20producing%20fabric%20from%20banana%20fibre%2C%20which%20boasts%20anti-microbial%20properties.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20anti-microbial%20properties%20of%20banana%20fibre%2C%20derived%20from%20natural%20compounds%20in%20the%20plant%2C%20create%20a%20protective%20shield%20on%20the%20fabric%2C%20inhibiting%20the%20growth%20of%20bacteria%20and%20fungi.%20This%20fabric%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20used%20in%20medical%20textiles%2C%20and%20efforts%20are%20underway%20to%20integrate%20additional%20functional%20properties%2C%20such%20as%20water%20resistance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-9-1733816042.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nengneithem%20Hengna%20(L)%20and%20Major%20Tanay%20Maben%20(R)%20-%20co-founders%20of%20Hengna%20%26amp%3B%20Maben%20Private%20Limited%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-9-1733816042.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-9-1733816042-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-9-1733816042-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-9-1733816042-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-9-1733816042-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-388032%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ENengneithem%20Hengna%20(L)%20and%20Major%20Tanay%20Maben%20(R)%20%E2%80%93%20co-founders%20of%20Hengna%20%26amp%3B%20Maben%20Private%20Limited%3B%20Image%20courtesy%3A%20Hengna%20%26amp%3B%20Maben%20Private%20Limited%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F354933%2Fombak-sustainable-furniture-shruthi-prakash-rattan-chairs-table-wall-decor-from-banana-fibres-in-indonesia-india%2F%5C%22%3EBanana%20fibre%20is%20also%20an%20eco-friendly%20alternative%20to%20polymer-based%20fabrics%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20it%20is%20biodegradable.%20Moreover%2C%20banana%20plants%20require%20minimal%20water%20and%20chemical%20inputs%2C%20including%20pesticides%20and%20fertilisers%2C%20making%20them%20a%20sustainable%20option%20compared%20to%20water-intensive%20cotton%2C%20explains%20Major%20Tanay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20the%20company%20produces%20handicrafts%20and%20packaging%20materials%20using%20banana%20fibre.%20With%20the%20goal%20of%20establishing%20banana%20fibre%20as%20a%20signature%20product%20of%20Nagaland%2C%20it%20has%20trained%20700%20artisans%20across%20Nagaland%20and%20other%20Northeast%20Indian%20states%20to%20create%20handmade%20items%20from%20the%20fibre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2Fho_0vUAs4-w%3Ffeature%3Doembed%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22281%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20founder%2C%20Nengneithem%20Hengna%2C%20who%20brings%2013%20years%20of%20experience%20in%20the%20handicrafts%20sector%2C%20began%20working%20with%20banana%20fibre%20in%202019.%20She%20experimented%20with%20different%20grades%20of%20fibre%2C%20braiding%20techniques%2C%20and%20stitching%20methods.%20She%20met%20Major%20Maben%20during%20COVID%20relief%20efforts%2C%20and%20they%20discovered%20shared%20goals.%20This%20collaboration%20led%20to%20the%20official%20incorporation%20of%20the%20company%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBanana%20is%20a%20zero-waste%20cash%20crop%20which%20yields%20a%20variety%20of%20products%20and%20by-products%20within%20a%20year%20of%20planting.%20It%20grows%20well%20in%20gently%20sloping%20terrain%20and%20is%20low-maintenance.%20Also%2C%20banana%20fibre%20is%20a%20very%20versatile%20fibre%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Major%20Tanay.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20coarser%20type%20can%20be%20used%20to%20make%20coasters%20while%20the%20delicate%20variety%20can%20be%20used%20to%20craft%20jewellery%20and%20hair%20extensions.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-6-1733816156.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Trained%20artisans%20across%20Nagaland%20and%20other%20Northeast%20Indian%20states%20create%20handmade%20items%20from%20banana%20fibre.%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-6-1733816156.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-6-1733816156-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-6-1733816156-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-6-1733816156-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-6-1733816156-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-388038%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ETrained%20artisans%20across%20Nagaland%20and%20other%20Northeast%20Indian%20states%20create%20handmade%20items%20from%20banana%20fibre%3B%20Image%20courtesy%3A%20Hengna%20%26amp%3B%20Maben%20Private%20Limited%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20banana%20%E2%80%98pseudostem%E2%80%99%20is%20passed%20through%20rollers%20(like%20in%20the%20case%20of%20sugarcane)%20and%20the%20mulch%20is%20extracted.%20What%20remains%20is%20the%20fibre%2C%20which%20is%20washed%2C%20dried%2C%20segregated%2C%20combed%20(to%20get%20various%20grades)%20and%20graded%2C%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20products%20made%20and%20sold%20by%20the%20company%20using%20banana%20fibre%20and%20bark%20are%20vases%2C%20planters%2C%20jewellery%2C%20bags%2C%20clutches%2C%20coasters%2C%20table%20mats%2C%20wall%20hangings%2C%20lanterns%20and%20baskets.%20The%20prices%20of%20these%20products%20range%20from%20Rs%20300%20to%20Rs%2010%2C000%2C%20says%20Nengneithem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-8_11zon-1733816737.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Products%20made%20using%20banana%20fibre.%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-8_11zon-1733816737.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-8_11zon-1733816737-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-8_11zon-1733816737-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-8_11zon-1733816737-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-8_11zon-1733816737-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-388050%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EProducts%20made%20using%20banana%20fibre%3B%20Image%20courtesy%3A%20Hengna%20%26amp%3B%20Maben%20Private%20Limited%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20two%20units%20in%20Dimapur%20and%20Athibung%2C%20employing%20over%2030%20artisans.%20We%20provide%20banana%20fibre%20and%20bark%20as%20eco-friendly%20fillers%20for%20packaging.%20We%20also%20use%20these%20materials%20to%20package%20our%20own%20handicrafts%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%20%E2%80%9COnce%20the%20product%20is%20delivered%2C%20customers%20can%20repurpose%20the%20fibre%20from%20the%20packaging%20in%20their%20gardens%2C%20as%20it%20provides%20valuable%20nutrients%20for%20plants.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERunway%20India%20has%20also%20explored%20creating%20paper%20from%20banana%20stem%20mulch.%20This%20paper%20is%20used%20for%20wrapping%20handicrafts%2C%20as%20well%20as%20in%20crafting%20greeting%20cards%20and%20flower%20bouquets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2Fo1Jdi9AQA4A%3Ffeature%3Doembed%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%222%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22281%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETraining%20and%20capacity%20building%20are%20central%20to%20the%20company%E2%80%99s%20mission.%20The%20enterprise%20has%20partnered%20with%20Assam%20Rifles%20to%20provide%20training%20to%20women%20in%20areas%20affected%20by%20poverty%20and%20insurgency.%20Additionally%2C%20it%20conducts%20workshops%20in%20schools%20as%20part%20of%20the%20National%20Education%20Policy%20(2020)%20skill%20development%20module.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E4.%20Light%2C%20sturdy%20bamboo%20composite%20boats%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECountry%20boats%20are%20prone%20to%20leaks%20and%20instability%2C%20leading%20to%20several%20fatal%20accidents%20each%20year.%20While%20fibre-glass%20boats%20are%20a%20common%20alternative%2C%20they%20are%20neither%20biodegradable%20nor%20recyclable%2C%20often%20ending%20up%20in%20rivers%20and%20causing%20significant%20environmental%20harm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20Ravi%20J%20Deka%20founded%20Akvotransiro%20Tech%20Pvt%20Ltd%20in%20Assam%20in%202020.%20His%20startup%20aims%20to%20revolutionise%20inland%20water%20transport%20by%20creating%20safer%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F337729%2Fbihar-bamboo-startup-entrepreneur-satyam-sundaram-eco-friendly-products-profits%2F%5C%22%3Eeco-friendly%20bamboo%3C%2Fa%3E%20composite%20boats%2C%20offering%20sustainable%20water%20mobility%20solutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20innovation%20took%20over%20two%20years%20to%20materialise.%20Our%20boats%20are%20made%20of%2085%20percent%20bamboo%2C%2010%20percent%20polymers%2C%20and%20five%20percent%20fibre-glass.%20The%20main%20advantage%20of%20bamboo%20composite%20boats%20is%20their%20sustainability.%20Bamboo%20is%20six%20times%20more%20sustainable%20than%20hardwood%20%E2%80%94%20it%E2%80%99s%20fast-growing%2C%20abundant%2C%20and%20incredibly%20strong%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ravi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-11-1733819460.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20glimpse%20into%20the%20boat-making%20process%20(L)%2C%20Ravi%20J%20Deka%20(R)%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-11-1733819460.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-11-1733819460-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-11-1733819460-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-11-1733819460-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-11-1733819460-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-388086%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EA%20glimpse%20into%20the%20boat-making%20process%20(L)%2C%20Ravi%20J%20Deka%20(R)%3B%20Image%20courtesy%3A%20Akvotransiro%20Tech%20Pvt%20Ltd%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBamboo%20composite%20boards%20are%20lightweight%2C%20cost-effective%2C%20and%20biodegradable%2C%20with%20an%20expected%20lifespan%20of%2010%20to%2015%20years.%20Their%20compressive%20strength%20and%20flexibility%20also%20provide%20better%20shock%20absorption%20compared%20to%20boats%20made%20from%20other%20materials%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnlike%20traditional%20wooden%20boats%2C%20which%20require%20trees%20to%20be%20felled%2C%20bamboo%20boats%20leave%20no%20such%20ecological%20footprint.%20Bamboo%20composite%20boats%20also%20have%20the%20lowest%20carbon%20footprint%20of%20any%20boat-making%20process%2C%20claims%20Deka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20bamboo%20composite%20boats%20are%2020%20to%2030%20percent%20more%20expensive%20than%20traditional%20wooden%20boats.%20For%20example%2C%20a%20wooden%20canoe%20for%20four%20people%20costs%20Rs%2060%2C000%2C%20while%20our%20boats%20range%20from%20Rs%2090%2C000%20for%20a%20four-person%20canoe%20to%20up%20to%20Rs%208%20lakh%20for%20a%20trimaran.%20However%2C%20our%20boats%20are%20half%20the%20price%20of%20fibre-glass%20boats%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20process%20of%20making%20the%20boats%20is%20labour-intensive.%20The%20core%20material%20consists%20of%20compressed%20bamboo%20mat%20boards%2C%20created%20by%20pressing%20layers%20of%20woven%20bamboo%20mats%20together%2C%20which%20are%20then%20joined%20to%20form%20the%20boats.%20Ravi%20has%20also%20innovated%20to%20strengthen%20these%20boards%20and%20make%20them%20waterproof.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-10-1733827742.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ravi%20Deka%20at%20work%20designing%20the%20boats%20(L)%3B%20A%20canoe%20made%20of%20bamboo%20composites%20(R)%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-10-1733827742.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-10-1733827742-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-10-1733827742-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-10-1733827742-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-10-1733827742-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-388179%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERavi%20Deka%20at%20work%20designing%20the%20boats%20(L)%3B%20A%20canoe%20made%20of%20bamboo%20composites%20(R)%3B%20Image%20courtesy%3A%20Akvotransiro%20Tech%20Pvt%20Ltd%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20boats%20are%2040%20to%2060%20percent%20lighter%20than%20their%20fibre-glass%20or%20wooden%20counterparts.%20With%20bamboo%20boats%2C%20you%20can%20achieve%20good%20speeds%20using%20less%20power%2C%20making%20them%20more%20efficient%20and%20lowering%20running%20costs%2C%20he%20further%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20was%20incubated%20at%20IIT%20Guwahati%20and%20has%20developed%20prototypes%20of%20six%20different%20types%20of%20bamboo%20composite%20boats%2C%20with%20patents%20pending.%20The%20smallest%20boat%20is%20a%20three-person%20canoe%2C%20while%20the%20company%20also%20manufactures%20canoes%20with%20outriggers%20%E2%80%94%20structures%20that%20enhance%20stability%20and%20improve%20manoeuvrability.%20The%20largest%20model%20is%20a%20trimaran%2C%20capable%20of%20carrying%2018%20passengers%20and%20two%20crew%20members.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20many%20potential%20applications%20for%20bamboo%20composite%20boats%2C%E2%80%9D%20continues%20Ravi.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20can%20serve%20as%20rescue%20boats%20during%20floods%2C%20transporting%20people%20and%20relief%20materials%2C%20particularly%20drinking%20water.%20They%20are%20ideal%20for%20forest%20patrolling%20in%20shallow%20waters%20and%20marshlands%2C%20as%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20get%20stuck%20in%20the%20mud.%20They%20offer%20an%20affordable%20option%20for%20fishermen%20and%20can%20function%20as%20small%20ferries%20or%20water%20taxis.%20Additionally%2C%20they%20could%20play%20a%20role%20in%20the%20eco-tourism%20sector%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20elaborates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20commercial%20production%20has%20yet%20to%20begin%2C%20the%20company%20has%20received%20inquiries%20from%20abroad%2C%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%